(1, 'AKASH Utshob', 'akash-utshob', '<p><strong>Campaign Timeline:</strong> 1st November - 30th November</p>\n\n<p><strong>Participant Eligibility Criteria:</strong></p>\n\n<p>Anyone buying AKASH DTH from our authorized retail outlets, direct sales and online within Bangladesh, and activating & recharging a minimum of BDT 399 for the month of November 2019.</p>\n\n<h6>Modality:</h6>\n\n<p><u>Contest Phase: There will be two phases of “AKASH UTSHOB” campaign, i.e. Weekly and Month End.</u></p>\n\n<p><strong>Weekly:</strong> All new subscribers who have bought and recharged a minimum of BDT 399 for AKASH in the 1st week of November will have to correctly answer a question through a quiz to be conducted via automated Interactive voice response (IVR) and first 250 to correctly answer in the shortest possible time will be selected as the winner on the basis of fastest finger first. Next week onwards (i.e. 2nd to 4th week of November 2019), AKASH* will select next 250 winners out of eligible participants in the same process described above. The winner and participant of a single week are not eligible to participate in the quiz for An SMS would be sent on November 8th, November 15th, November 22nd, December 3rd and eligible participants would have to give a missed call in the provided number and against their missed call the participant will get automatic computer generated call through which participant will require to answer a single question and winner would be selected on Fastest Finger First basis. Participants would be allowed a maximum of 48 hours to participate from the time participant receives weekly quiz eligibility confirmation SMS.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Month End Grand Quiz:</strong> All new subscribers, including all eligible participants from 1st week to 4th week of November 2019 will be eligible to participate in the final quiz held on 6th December, 2019.</p>\n\n<p>An SMS would be sent on December 6th eligible participants would have to give a missed call in the provided number and against their missed call the participant will get automatic computer generated call through which participant will require to answer 3 questions and winner would be selected on Fastest Finger First basis. Participants would be allowed a maximum of 48 hours to participate from time participant receives month-end grand quiz eligibility confirmation SMS.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Winner Announcement:</strong> Through SMS and Facebook page of <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/AkashDTHBangladesh\" target=\"_blank\">AKASH DTH</a>.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Available Prizes:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>International Tour Packages (For 2)- Egypt Tour, Malaysia and Thailand</li>\n	<li>International Air Tickets (For 2)- Dhaka -Kolkata- Dhaka</li>\n	<li>LED TV- 32”, 43” and 55”</li>\n	<li>Free Set Top Box (STB)</li>\n	<li>Free 1-Month Subscription</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Rules:</h3>\n\n<ol>\n	<li>Subscriber must activate and recharge for 1-month subscription to be eligible for the AKASH UTSHOB quiz, eligible participants will get a SMS, they have to give a ‘missed call’ on the provided number to take part in the quiz.</li>\n	<li>The quiz will be based on Interactive voice response (IVR) and the participant needs follow the instructions and respond accordingly.</li>\n	<li>There will be 1 question for the weekly prize contest and 3 questions for the grand prize contest.</li>\n	<li>Participants must participate in the contest within the next 48 hours (2 days) from the day they received the eligibility confirmation SMS. Late response will result in disqualification. (As soon as AKASH gets the top 250 winners list based on the preset criteria, the contest will be closed for that respective week)</li>\n	<li>List of Top 250 winners will be published on weekly basis and Top 3 Grand Prize Winners list will be also published at the end of the campaign. Winner names will be announced based on the number of right answers and based on fastest response time.</li>\n	<li>Purchasers recharging on 2nd December or later will not be eligible for the campaign.</li>\n</ol>\n\n<h3>Terms and Conditions:</h3>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><u>“AKASH UTSHOB” campaign</u> will be held from 1<sup>st</sup> November – 30<sup>th</sup> November, 2019.</li>\n	<li>The special promotional price of BDT 5,499 will remain valid until further notice.</li>\n	<li>Purchaser will get 10 meters’ length of cable with every unit of AKASH DTH CPE that contains STB, Dish, Remote, LNB (please add other components)</li>\n	<li>The purchaser must be Bangladeshi (Nationality) to be eligible for the campaign.</li>\n	<li>During the AKASH UTSHOB campaign the monthly subscription price will remain BDT 399. Minimum of 1-month of Subscription Fee (i.e. BDT 399) must be recharged to be eligible for the campaign.</li>\n	<li>Other special promotion EMI purchases will be eligible for AKASH UTSHOB campaign.</li>\n	<li>Anyone buying, AKASH DTH connection (Full CPE unit or only STB) from authorized retail outlets and online (Incl. through EMI option and direct sales) within Bangladesh, and activating & recharging for the month on November 2019 are eligible for the campaign.</li>\n	<li>Subscribers who bought AKASH DTH before November 2019 and activating and recharging on the month of November 2019 will not be allowed to participate in the campaign.</li>\n	<li>Customer purchasing only STB are also eligible to participate in the campaign.</li>\n	<li>Existing AKASH DTH subscribers or inactive customer are not eligible to participate in the campaign.</li>\n	<li>Only the valid registered subscriber will be entitled for the Prize, no one else can collect prize on behalf of the subscriber.</li>\n	<li>People purchasing product on 30<sup>th</sup> November 2019, but recharging on 2<sup>nd</sup> December or later will not be eligible for the campaign.</li>\n	<li>Participants recharging on a particular week will only be allowed to participate for that specific week quiz.</li>\n	<li>In case of call drop during the weekly/monthly quiz through IVR, participant will be allowed up to 5 times to re-enter the quiz through missed call.</li>\n	<li>Entitled winner can collect their prizes from nearest regional offices on pre-specified date of AKASH.</li>\n	<li>All the air tickets mentioned in the prizes list will be of Economic class, upgradation to business class will not be allowed in any conditions.</li>\n	<li>Air tickets and tour packages will come in dual package form (for 2 person)</li>\n	<li>Prizes won are not transferable and cannot be combined with any other prize or any other offer or discounts or promotions offered by AKASH.</li>\n	<li>All offers (e.g. Specific Model of TV, Foreign Tour Package) are subject to availability, it might not be available due to exhaustion of existing stock or due to political instability, natural calamities, in such cases prizes will be replaced by other available prizes of same monetary value.</li>\n	<li>The winner needs to show the Winner confirmation SMS from AKASH and have valid identity card and proof of ownership of the registered number in order to collect the entitled prize.</li>\n	<li>Beximco Communications Ltd. (AKASH DTH) assures its customers/subscribers that, there is no financial investment, deposit, security money required to enter AKASH UTSHOB quiz contest, all the customers/subscribers are requested to remain cautious for any such type of fraudulent offer. <em>(Beximco Communications Ltd. won’t be responsible for any kind of personal or financial loss due to any fraudulent incident)</em></li>\n	<li>No transportation allowance would be provided to winners when collecting the prize.</li>\n	<li>By participating, the subscriber/purchaser agrees to be bound by these Terms & Conditions. Subscriber /purchaser must comply with these Terms & Conditions to be able to receive prize at the end of this campaign.</li>\n	<li>All customers have to sign the SAF Acknowledgment at the time of purchasing AKASH DTH.</li>\n	<li>AKASH reserves all the right to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</li>\n	<li>AKASH shall not be liable for any loss, damage or injury suffered or sustained (even if caused by negligence) as a result of accepting and/or using the prize, except for any liability which cannot be excluded by law.</li>\n	<li>AKASH accepts no responsibility for late, lost or misdirected SMS or other communications. AKASH assumes no responsibility for any failure to receive a claim or for inaccurate information or for any loss, damage or injury as a result of technical or telecommunications problems, including security breaches. If such problems arise, then AKASH may modify, cancel, terminate or suspend the prize handover process.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>AKASH shall mean Beximco Communications Limited</p>\n\n<p>The AKASH UTSHOB” campaign will be held from 1st November - 30th November, 2019.</p>\n\n<p>For details, please visit our website <a href=\"https://akashdth.com/\"><strong>www.akashdth.com</strong></a> or <strong>call 16442.</strong></p>\n', '1572527605-15043188.jpg', '1572527605-93281661.jpg', '', 'Promotional', 0, 0, 0, '2020-05-10 16:00:00', '2020-12-10 16:00:00', '2020-02-01 10:50:37', '2019-10-31 19:13:25', ''),
(2, 'Free Installation And/Or Free Subscription', 'free-installation-free-subscription', '<p><span style=\"font-size:21px\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Details of the offer:</span></strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:21px\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">The ongoing Promotional Offer of Free Installation and/or Free Subscription Fee at the time of purchase of AKASH DTH connection. </span></strong></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:black\">Terms and Conditions in respect of Free Installation and/or Free Subscription Fee:</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ol>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;The Subscriber will be eligible for Promotional Offer of Free Installation of CPE/STB and/or Free Subscription Fee for any period as determined by AKASH from time to time, if only if, s/he subscribes to the AKASH service for a minimum period of 12 months from the date of service activation. If the Subscriber returns the CPE/STB within 12 months from the date of service activation, then, please refer to &ldquo;<a href=\"https://akashdth.com/refund-policy\" target=\"_blank\">Refund Policy</a>&rdquo; as provided in this website. </span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ol start=\"2\">\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;Promotional Offer of Free Installation of CPE/STB and/or Free Subscription Fee will only be valid for 15 (fifteen) days from the date of creation of Subscriber ID (the &ldquo;Validity Period&rdquo;) in respect of the Subscriber who wishes to avail the Promotional Offer of Free Installation of CPE/STB and/or Free Subscription Fee as given by AKASH.&nbsp; In any event, if the Subscriber does not avail the Promotional Offer of Free Installation of CPE/STB and/or Free Subscription Fee within the said Validity