(4, 'AKASH DTH REFERRAL', 'referral', '<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">When an AKASH subscriber refers AKASH to a potential customer, referrer will get 100 taka cashback in his/her AKASH account if referee gets AKASH Standard Package. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Campaign Timeline: </strong>1 – 31 January 2023</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>Terms & Conditions:</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Only Referrer will get Tk.100 cashback in his/her AKASH account if referee buys Standard package after referring new connection lead through contact center channel or MY AKASH APP</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Referred Sales lead must be confirmed, account is activated and recharge is made (e. g. One-month full subscription fees) in newly created Referee’s account.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Sales Lead must need to be completed/ fulfilled (i.e., Purchase, Activate and Recharge) within 7th Day of following month from the Referred Date (Lead Issue date). Examples:</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Scenario 01: If any Referrer refers a lead on 01-Jan-2023, that lead must be completed the steps of Purchase, Activation and Recharge within 07-Feb-2023</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Scenario 02: If any Referrer refers a lead on 15-Jan-2023, that lead must be completed the steps of Purchase, Activation and Recharge within 07-Feb-2023</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Scenario 03: If any Referrer refers a lead on 31-Jan-2023, that lead must be completed the steps of Purchase, Activation and Recharge within 07-Feb-2023</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">One subscriber can get maximum Tk. 500 as referrer in a calendar month or 5 referrals in a month based on Referred date (Lead Issue date)</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Referral bonus will be disbursed within 10 working days after the required recharge in newly created Referee’s account.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">AKASH reserves all rights to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '1674118563-89444603.jpg', '1674118564-37892115.jpg', '1674354644-57858301.png', 'Offer', 1, 1, 1, '2021-11-01 00:00:00', '2023-01-31 23:55:00', '2023-01-22 08:30:44', '2019-12-22 19:15:55', '');
