(5, 'AKASH DTH BPL GIVEAWAY', 'bpl-giveaway', '<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Campaign Timeline:</strong> 22<sup>nd</sup> December – 17<sup>th</sup> January, 2020 </span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Participant Eligibility and Modality: </strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Anyone buying AKASH DTH from our authorized retail outlets, direct sales and online within Bangladesh, and activating within the campaign period (22<sup>nd</sup> December to 17<sup>th</sup> January, 2020) are eligible for the campaign.</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Exclusive cricket bat, ball signed by the BPL team captains and Semi Final and Final tickets will be distributed among the lucky winners (randomly selected).</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Winner Announcement:</strong> Through SMS and Facebook page of AKASH DTH (After end of the campaign)</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><u>Available Prizes:</u></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<ol>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">BPL Captain’s Signed Bat</span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">BPL Captain’s Signed Ball</span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Semi Final and Final Match Tickets</span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">​<strong><u>TERMS & CONDITIONS</u></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">AKASH BPL Campaign will remain active from 22<sup>nd</sup> December – 17<sup>th</sup> January, 2020. </span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">The purchaser must be Bangladeshi (Nationality) to be eligible for the campaign. </span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Anyone purchasing full AKASH connection (CPE) or only the STB from authorized retail outlets and online (Incl. through EMI, FnF Package and Corporate Offer) within Bangladesh, and activating during the campaign period are eligible for the campaign.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Retailer/Distributor of AKASH (Beximco Communications Ltd.) are not eligible to participate.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Employees of Beximco Communications Limited are not eligible, however their parents, siblings, spouses & children, friends are eligible to participate.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Existing AKASH DTH subscribers or inactive customer are not eligible to participate in the campaign, however they can participate through purchase of new AKASH connection during the campaign period (22<sup>nd</sup> December 2019 to 17<sup>th</sup> January 2020)</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Prizes will be distributed after the end of the campaign, AKASH team will inform the winners regarding the prize distribution date and prize collection process.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Only the people purchasing and activating AKASH connection till 11<sup>th</sup> Jan 2020 will be eligible for the match tickets (Semi and Final) and the ticket winner names will be announced on 12<sup>th</sup> January 2020. The winners will be informed via SMS and a winner list will be also published on Facebook page. Winners needs collect the match tickets from Beximco Communication Ltd. Dhaka-Head office before 17<sup>th</sup> January 2020.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Only the valid registered subscriber will be entitled for the Prize, no one else can collect prize on behalf of the subscriber. </span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">People purchasing product before 22<sup>nd</sup> December 2019, but activating during the campaign period (22<sup>nd</sup> December 2019 to 17<sup>th</sup> January 2020) are not be eligible for the campaign.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">AKASH (Beximco Communications Ltd.) assures its customers/subscribers that, there is no financial investment, deposit, security money required to enter AKASH BPL Campaign, all the customers/subscribers are requested to remain cautious for any such type of fraudulent offer. <em><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\">(Beximco Communications Ltd. won’t be responsible for any kind of personal or financial loss due to any fraudulent incident)</span></em></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">No transportation allowance would be provided to winners when collecting the prize. </span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">By participating, the subscriber/purchaser agrees to be bound by these Terms & Conditions. Subscriber /purchaser must comply with these Terms & Conditions to be able to receive prize at the end of this campaign.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">AKASH (Beximco Communications Ltd.) reserves all the right to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">AKASH (Beximco Communications Ltd.) shall not be liable for any loss, damage or injury suffered or sustained (even if caused by negligence) as a result of accepting and/or using the prize, except for any liability which cannot be excluded by law.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">People purchasing and activating AKASH connection till 11<sup>th</sup> Jan 2020, will only be eligible for the match tickets (e.g. Qualifier, Eliminator and Final) and the ticket winner names will be announced from 12<sup>th</sup> to 15<sup>th</sup> January 2020 for the respective matches. The winners will be informed via SMS and call regarding the collection process of their match ticket.</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">​<u> </u><strong><u><span style=\"font-size:24.0pt\">FAQ</span></u></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">What is AKASH BPL Campaign?</span></strong></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Ans:</span></strong><span style=\"color:black\"> AKASH always strives to make the magical AKASH experience the most rewarding experience for you!  AKASH has more than 40 HD channels and more than 115 total channels, soon there\'ll be even more! Anyone buying AKASH DTH from our authorized retail outlets, direct sales and online within Bangladesh, and activating during the campaign period (22nd December 2019 to 17th January, 2020) are eligible for the campaign and among the eligible participants more than 150 lucky winners will get exclusive cricket bat or ball signed by the BPL team captains or BPL Semi Final or Final tickets.   </span></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">How long is the duration of this campaign?</span></strong></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Ans:</span></strong><span style=\"color:black\"> The campaign will run from 22nd December 2019 to 17th January 2020. You have to purchase an AKASH Connection, activate within the time frame to participate in this campaign.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">If I purchase only STB, will I be eligible to participate?</span></strong></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Ans:</span></strong><span style=\"color:black\"> Yes! If you purchase the full AKASH connection or only the STB, activate, you\'ll be eligible to participate in the campaign! You\'ll have to buy the STB or the full connection from 22<sup>nd</sup> December 2019 to 17th January 2020 otherwise you won\'t be eligible.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">I\'m a current subscriber of AKASH. Am I eligible to participate?</span></strong></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Ans:</span></strong><span style=\"color:black\"> No, only subscribers purchasing the full connection or the STB from 22nd December to 17th January are eligible to participate. If you have purchased AKASH before December 22nd 2019, you can still participate in the campaign by buying additional connections or STBs during 22nd December 2019 to 17th January 2020!</span></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Do I need to recharge after activating my connection to participate in this campaign?  </span></strong></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Ans:</span></strong><span style=\"color:black\"> No you don\'t need to recharge. Existing or new customers purchasing the full connection or the STB from 22nd December 2019 to 17th January 2020 and activating during this specified campaign period are eligible to participate.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">I bought AKASH Connection/STB before 22nd December 2019 but my installation has been completed on or after 22nd December 2019; am I eligible for the campaign?</span></strong></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Ans: </span></strong><span style=\"color:black\">No, only subscribers purchasing and activating the full connection or the STB from 22nd December 2019 to 17th January 2020 are eligible to participate. If you have purchased AKASH before 22nd December, you can still participate in the campaign by buying additional connections or STBs during 22nd December 2019 to 17th January 2020!</span></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">I was a Real VU subscriber. Will I be eligible to participate?</span></strong></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Ans:</span></strong><span style=\"color:black\"> Yes. Any Bangladeshi citizen will be eligible to participate if he buys a new AKASH Connection or STB within 22nd December 2019 to 17th January 2020.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">I bought AKASH Connection/STB before 22nd December 2019 but my installation has been completed on or after 22nd December 2019; am I eligible for the campaign?</span></strong></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Ans: </span></strong><span style=\"color:black\">No, only subscribers purchasing and activating the full connection or the STB from 22nd December 2019 to 17th January 2020 are eligible to participate. If you have purchased AKASH before 22nd December, you can still participate in the campaign by buying additional connections or STBs during 22nd December 2019 to 17th January 2020!</span></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">I was a Real VU subscriber. Will I be eligible to participate?</span></strong></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Ans:</span></strong><span style=\"color:black\"> Yes. Any Bangladeshi citizen will be eligible to participate if he buys a new AKASH Connection or STB within 22nd December 2019 to 17th January 2020.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">I\'m an employee of AKASH/Beximco Communications Limited. Will I be eligible to participate?</span></strong></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Ans:</span></strong><span style=\"color:black\"> Employees of Beximco Communications Limited are not eligible, however their parents, siblings, spouses & children, friends are eligible to participate.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">If I purchase through EMI within 22nd December 2019 to 17th January 2020, will I be eligible?</span></strong></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Ans: </span></strong><span style=\"color:black\">Yes! You will be eligible if you purchase full AKASH connection or STB through EMI, Online or any authorized retail points within 22nd December to 17th January 2020.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">If I purchase STB/full AKASH Connection through online, will I be eligible?</span></strong></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Ans:</span></strong><span style=\"color:black\"> Yes! You will be eligible if you purchase full AKASH connection or STB through EMI, Online or any authorized retail points within 22nd December to 17th January 2020.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">I am a retailer/Distributor of AKASH. Am I eligible for this contest/How can I participate in this contest?</span></strong></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Ans:</span></strong><span style=\"color:black\"> No, you cannot participate in the contest for new AKASH Subscribers only. </span></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">I purchased AKASH connection from 22nd December to 17th January 2020 from corporate offer. Am I eligible to participate?</span></strong></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Ans: </span></strong><span style=\"color:black\">Yes! You will be eligible if you activate no later than 17th January 2020.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">I purchased the AKASH connection/STB & activated within 22nd December 2019 to 17th December 2020. If I recharge for 6 months or 12 months, am I eligible?</span></strong></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Ans:</span></strong><span style=\"color:black\"> You don\'t need to recharge any amount to participate, if you just purchase and activate your AKASH connection within 22nd December 2019 to 17th January 2020, you\'re eligible for the campaign.  </span></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">I purchased AKASH connection within 22nd December to 17th January 2020 through employee FnF offer. Am I eligible to participate?</span></strong></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Ans:</span></strong><span style=\"color:black\"> Yes! You will be eligible if you activate no later than 17th January 2020.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">How can I participate in the quiz?</span></strong></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Ans:</span></strong><span style=\"color:black\"> If you have purchased AKASH DTH from our authorized retail outlets, direct sales and online within Bangladesh, and activating within the campaign period (22nd December to 17th January, 2020) are eligible for the campaign and among the eligible participants more than 150 lucky winners will get exclusive cricket bat or ball signed by the BPL team captains or BPL Semi Final or Final tickets. There\'s no requirement for any additional recharge or answer any quiz questions. Winners will be selected randomly based on the lucky draw after the end of the campaign and the winners will be communicated by team AKASH regarding the collection process and dates.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">If I purchase multiple connections, will my chances of winning increase?</span></strong></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Ans:</span></strong><span style=\"color:black\"> Yes, more new AKASH DTH connections you buy your chances of winning will be higher.     </span></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">How will the winners be decided? /Based on what the winners will be decided?</span></strong></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Ans: </span></strong><span style=\"color:black\">Winners will be decided based on a lucky draw </span></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">What will be the CPE Price/STB Price/Package price during the campaign?</span></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Ans:</span></strong><span style=\"color:black\"> AKASH Connection is available at only BDT 5499 & only STB is available at BDT 3799 now! These prices will also be valid for the campaign period. The BDT 399 subscription fee of AKASH Standard Package will also remain valid. To sum up, there\'s no change in prices or offers during these campaign.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Will the free subscription period of 5 days be available during the campaign?</span></strong></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Ans:</span></strong><span style=\"color:black\"> Yes, new subscribers during the campaign period will be eligible for the 5-day free subscription period.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">What are prizes of this BPL Campaign?</span></strong></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Ans:</span></strong><span style=\"color:black\"> Exclusive cricket bat or ball signed by the BPL team captains or BPL Semi Final or Final tickets.   </span></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Can a winner win multiple prizes?</span></strong></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Ans:</span></strong><span style=\"color:black\"> No, each participant is eligible to win only one prize. </span></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">How will the winners know that they have won the prizes?</span></strong></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Ans:</span></strong><span style=\"color:black\"> All winners will get SMS to their registered mobile number & we\'ll also call them to inform them about further details of the prizes.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">How will I collect the prizes?</span></strong></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Ans:</span></strong><span style=\"color:black\"> The winners will get a call from us regarding further details of the prizes and prize collection process.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Do I need to come physically to collect the prizes?</span></strong></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Ans: </span></strong><span style=\"color:black\">Yes, only the valid registered subscriber will be entitled for the Prize, no one else can collect prize on behalf of the subscriber </span></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">What do I need to bring to collect prizes?</span></strong></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Ans:</span></strong><span style=\"color:black\"> The winner needs to show the Winner confirmation SMS from AKASH and have valid identity card and proof of ownership of the registered number in order to collect the entitled prize. Details will be communicated to the winners at the time we call the winners.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Will I get SMS/any notification if I don\'t win any prizes?</span></strong></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Ans:</span></strong><span style=\"color:black\"> No, only the winners will be notified.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Will the winners get any transportation allowance for visiting the designated point to collect the prizes?</span></strong></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Ans: </span></strong><span style=\"color:black\">No transportation allowance would be provided to winners when collecting the prize</span></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Can I get the equivalent cash amount for the prize won?</span></strong></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Ans:</span></strong><span style=\"color:black\"> Prizes won are not transferable and cannot be combined with any other prize or any other offer or discounts or promotions offered by AKASH. Only in the events of exhaustion of existing stock or due to political instability, natural calamities, in such cases prizes will be replaced by other available prizes of same monetary value</span></span></span></p>\n', '1577021050-37562047.jpg', '1577021050-75021253.jpg', '', 'Promotional', 0, 0, 0, '2020-05-10 16:00:00', '2020-12-10 16:00:00', '2020-02-01 11:02:41', '2019-12-22 19:24:10', ''),
(6, 'BPL Campaign with Daraz', 'bpl-campaign-with-daraz', '<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Campaign Timeline:</strong> 22<sup>nd</sup> December – 17<sup>th</sup> January, 2020 </span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Participant Eligibility and Modality: </strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Anyone buying AKASH DTH from Daraz platform and activating within the campaign period (22<sup>nd</sup> December to 17<sup>th</sup> January, 2020) are eligible for the campaign.</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Other than guaranteed 1-month free subscription, purchasers of AKASH DTH connection from Daraz will also get chance to win exclusive cricket ball signed by the BPL team captains through a lucky draw (After the end of the campaign).</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Winner Announcement:</strong> Through SMS and Facebook page of AKASH DTH (After end of the campaign)</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><u>Available Prizes other than Confirm 1-Month Free Subscription:</u></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<ol>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">BPL Captain’s Signed Ball (Only)</span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">​<strong><u>TERMS & CONDITIONS</u></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">AKASH BPL Daraz Campaign will remain active from 22<sup>nd</sup> December – 17<sup>th</sup> January, 2020. </span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">The purchaser must be Bangladeshi (Nationality) to be eligible for the campaign. </span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Anyone purchasing full AKASH connection (CPE) or only the STB from Daraz, and activating during the campaign period are eligible for the campaign.</span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Other terms and conditions set by daraz for purchase of products through their platform will be applicable</span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Existing AKASH DTH subscribers or inactive customer are not eligible to participate in the campaign, however they can participate through purchase of new AKASH connection during the campaign period (22nd December 2019 to 17th January 2020)</span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Prizes will be distributed after the end of the campaign, AKASH team will inform the winners regarding the prize distribution date and prize collection process.</span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Only the valid registered subscriber will be entitled for the Prize, no one else can collect prize on behalf of the subscriber. </span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">People purchasing product before 22nd December 2019, but activating during the campaign period (22nd December 2019 to 17th January 2020) are not be eligible for the campaign.</span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">AKASH (Beximco Communications Ltd.) and Daraz reserves all the right to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">No travel allowance will be provided to the winners, for collecting their prizes from AKASH (Beximco Communications Ltd.)</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', '1577083617-39049529.jpg', '1577083617-87091580.jpg', '', 'Promotional', 0, 0, 0, '2020-05-10 16:00:00', '2020-12-10 16:00:00', '2020-02-02 10:36:51', '2019-12-23 12:46:57', '');
