(10, 'Valentines Day Campaign with Daraz', 'valentines-day-campaign-with-daraz', '<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">On the occasion of valentine’s day, if you buy AKASH DTH connection from Daraz, you will get 1 month’s free subscription. In addition, 5 lucky winners will also get couple (2 pcs’) movie tickets. </span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Moreover, if anyone buys any product from Daraz during this campaign he/she will get chance to win full AKASH DTH connection for free.</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Campaign Period: Feb 1, 2020 – Feb 14, 2020</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">*Condition: You have to buy the AKASH DTH (for one month’s free subscription and 5 couple movie tickets) or any other product from Daraz  (for full setup) during the campaign period.</span></span></p>\n', '1581402843-4704820.jpg', '1581402843-38396477.jpg', '', 'Promotional', 0, 0, 0, '2020-05-10 16:00:00', '2020-12-10 16:00:00', '2020-02-16 10:34:55', '2020-02-11 12:34:03', ''),
(11, 'Women’s T20 World Cup Giveaway Campaign', 'women-t20', '<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Campaign Timeline:</strong> February 21, 2020– March 8, 2020</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Participant Eligibility and Modality: </strong>Anyone buying and activating AKASH DTH from our authorized retail outlets, direct sales and AKASH website within Bangladesh, during the campaign period (February 21, 2020– March 8, 2020) are eligible to participate in the campaign and winners will be  selected based on lucky draw (randomly). </span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Available Prizes/Rewards: </strong></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Lucky winners will get exclusive cricket bat and ball signed by the National Women’s Cricket Team players and </span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Lucky winners will get chance to have dinner with the players <em>(Winners of Bat/Ball are not eligible for this reward)</em></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Winner Announcement: </strong></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Step 1: </strong>Through SMS </span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Step 2: </strong>Outbound Calls to the Winners </span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Step 3:</strong> Winner list Publish on Facebook page of AKASH DTH (After end of the campaign)</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"background-color:yellow\">​</span><strong>Prize/Reward Collection: </strong>All the winners must collect their respective rewards/prizes from Beximco Communication Ltd. Dhaka head office (Address-SAM Tower (Level 9), Plot-4, Road-22, Gulshan-1, Dhaka). Mr. G. M. Sadman Tanvir (Marketing Manager – Trade) will be the contact person for the prize handover process. </span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Terms & Conditions:</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Women’s T20 World Cup Giveaway Campaign will remain active from February 21, 2020 to March 8, 2020.</span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">The purchaser must be Bangladeshi (Nationality) to be eligible for the campaign.</span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Anyone purchasing full AKASH connection (CPE) or only the STB from authorized retail outlets and online (Incl. through EMI, FnF Package and Corporate Offer) within Bangladesh, and activating during the mentioned timeline are eligible for the campaign.</span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">FOC subscribers, Retailer/Distributor of AKASH (Beximco Communications Ltd.) are not eligible to participate.</span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Employees of Beximco Communications Limited are not eligible, however their parents, siblings, spouses & children, friends are eligible to participate.</span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Existing AKASH DTH subscribers or inactive customer are not eligible to participate in the campaign, however they can participate through purchase of new AKASH connection during the campaign period (February 21, 2020 to March 8, 2020).</span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Prizes will be distributed after the end of the campaign; AKASH team will inform the winners regarding the prize distribution date and prize collection process.</span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Only the valid registered subscriber will be entitled for the Prize, no one else can collect prize on behalf of the subscriber.</span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">People purchasing product before 21<sup>st</sup> February 2020, but activating during the campaign period (February 21, 2020 to March 8, 2020) are not be eligible for the campaign.</span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Winners of one category of prizes (Bat/Ball) will not be able to win other categories of prizes.</span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">AKASH (Beximco Communications Ltd.) assures its customers/subscribers that, there is no financial investment, deposit, security money required to enter AKASH Women’s T20 World Cup Giveaway Campaign, all the customers/subscribers are requested to remain cautious for any such type of fraudulent offer. (Beximco Communications Ltd. won’t be responsible for any kind of personal or financial loss due to any fraudulent incident)</span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">No transportation allowance would be provided to winners when collecting the prize.</span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">By participating, the subscriber/purchaser agrees to be bound by these Terms & Conditions. Subscriber /purchaser must comply with these Terms & Conditions to be able to receive prize at the end of this campaign.</span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">AKASH (Beximco Communications Ltd.) reserves all the right to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">AKASH (Beximco Communications Ltd.) shall not be liable for any loss, damage or injury suffered or sustained (even if caused by negligence) as a result of accepting and/or using the prize, except for any liability which cannot be excluded by law.</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">​<strong>Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ):</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>What is Women’s T20 World Cup Giveaway Campaign?</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Ans:</strong> AKASH always strives to make AKASH purchase experience more rewarding for its customers. Therefore, this time we came up with the “Women’s T20 World Cup Giveaway Campaign’. Anyone buying and activating AKASH DTH from our authorized retail outlets, direct sales and AKASH website within Bangladesh, during the campaign period (February 21, 2020– March 8, 2020) are eligible to participate in the campaign and winners will be  selected based on lottery (randomly).</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>How long is the duration of this campaign?</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Ans:</strong> The campaign will run February 21, 2020– March 8, 2020. Customers must purchase new AKASH Connection (STB/Full CPE Unit) and activate to be eligible for the campaign.</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>If I purchase only STB, will I be eligible to participate?</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Ans:</strong> Yes! If customers purchase the full AKASH connection or only the STB and activate, will be eligible to participate in the campaign.</span></span></p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>I\'m a current subscriber of AKASH. Am I eligible to participate?</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Ans:</strong> No, only subscribers purchasing the full connection or the STB from February 21, 2020– March 8, 2020 and activating are eligible to participate. If you have purchased AKASH before 21<sup>st</sup> February 2020, you can still participate in the campaign by buying additional full connections or STBs during the campaign period.</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Do I need to recharge after activating my connection to participate in this campaign? </strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Ans:</strong> No you don\'t need to recharge. Existing or new customers purchasing the full connection or the STB from February 21, 2020– March 8, 2020 and activating during campaign period are eligible to participate.</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>I bought AKASH Connection/STB before 21<sup>st</sup> February 2020 but my installation has been completed after 8<sup>th</sup> March 2020; am I eligible for the campaign?</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Ans:</strong> No, only subscribers purchasing the full connection or the STB from February 21, 2020– March 8, 2020 and activating during campaign period are eligible to participate.</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>I was a Real VU subscriber. Will I be eligible to participate?</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Ans:</strong> Yes. Any Bangladeshi citizen will be eligible to participate if he buys a new AKASH Connection or STB during the campaign period.</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>I\'m an employee of AKASH/Beximco Communications Limited. Will I be eligible to participate?</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Ans: </strong>Employees of Beximco Communications Limited are not eligible, however their parents, siblings, spouses & children, friends are eligible to participate.</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>If I purchase through EMI within February 21, 2020– March 8, 2020, will I be eligible?</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Ans: </strong>Yes! You will be eligible if you purchase full AKASH connection or STB through EMI, AKASH website or any authorized retail points during the campaign period. </span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>If I purchase STB/full AKASH Connection through online (AKASH Website only), will I be eligible?</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Ans: </strong>Yes! You will be eligible if you purchase full AKASH connection or STB through EMI, AKASH website or any authorized retail points during the campaign period. <em>(However, not applicable for purchases done through third party E-commerce sites- Daraz, Pickaboo etc.)</em></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>I am a retailer/Distributor of AKASH. Am I eligible for this contest/How can I participate in this contest?</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Ans:</strong> No, you cannot participate in the campaign.</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>I purchased AKASH connection from February 21, 2020– March 8, 2020 from corporate offer. Am I eligible to participate?</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Ans:</strong> Yes! You will be eligible.</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>I purchased AKASH connection within February 21, 2020– March 8, 2020  through employee FnF offer. Am I eligible to participate?</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Ans:</strong> Yes! You will be eligible.</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>If I purchase multiple connections, will my chances of winning increase?</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Ans:</strong> Yes, more new AKASH DTH connections you buy your chances of winning will be higher.    </span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>How will the winners be decided? /Based on what the winners will be decided?</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Ans: </strong>Winners will be decided based on a lucky draw.</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>What will be the CPE Price/STB Price/Package price during the campaign?</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Ans:</strong> AKASH Connection is available at only BDT 5499 & only STB is available at BDT 3199 now! These prices will also be valid for the campaign period. The BDT 399 subscription fee of AKASH Standard  package will also remain valid. </span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Will the free subscription period of 5 days be available during the campaign?</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Ans:</strong> Yes, new subscribers during the campaign period will be eligible for the 5-day free subscription period.</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>What are prizes of this this Campaign?</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Ans:</strong> Exclusive cricket bat or ball signed by the National Women’s Cricket player and chance to have dinner with the players. </span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Can a winner win multiple prizes?</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Ans:</strong> No, each participant is eligible to win only one prize/reward.</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>How will the winners know that they have won the prizes?</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Ans:</strong> All winners will get SMS to their registered mobile number; AKASH team will reach out to the winners through outbound calls and at the end of the campaign winner names will be published on AKASH official Facebook page.</span></span></p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>How will I collect the prizes?</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Ans:</strong> All the winners must collect their respective rewards/prizes from Beximco Communication Ltd. Dhaka head office (Address-SAM Tower (Level 9), Plot-4, Road-22, Gulshan-1, Dhaka). Mr. G. M. Sadman Tanvir (Marketing Manager – Trade) will be the contact person for the prize handover process.</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Do I need to come physically to collect the prizes?</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Ans:</strong> Yes, only the valid registered subscriber will be entitled for the Prize, no one else can collect prize on behalf of the subscriber</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>What do I need to bring to collect prizes?</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Ans:</strong> The winner needs to show the Winner confirmation SMS from AKASH and have valid identity card and proof of ownership of the registered number in order to collect the entitled prize. Details will be communicated to the winners at the time we call the winners.</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Will I get SMS/any notification if I don\'t win any prizes?</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Ans:</strong> No, only the winners will be notified.</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Will the winners get any transportation allowance for visiting the designated point to collect the prizes?</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Ans:</strong> No transportation allowance would be provided to winners when collecting the prize</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Which cricketers will attend the dinner?</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Ans:</strong> Only Selective senior players approved by BCB.</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Can I get the equivalent cash amount for the prize won?</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Ans:</strong> Prizes won are not transferable and cannot be combined with any other prize or any other offer or discounts or promotions offered by AKASH. Only in the events of exhaustion of existing stock or due to political instability, natural calamities, in such cases prizes will be replaced by other available prizes of same monetary value</span></span></p>\n', '1582357639-21997228.jpg', '1582357639-12242711.jpg', '', 'Promotional', 0, 0, 0, '2020-05-10 16:00:00', '2020-12-10 16:00:00', '2020-04-14 20:26:24', '2020-02-22 13:47:19', '');
