(12, 'CRICKET BAT AND JERSEY GIVEAWAY CAMPAIGN', 'bat-jersey-cricket', '<p style=\"text-align:center\"> </p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Campaign Timeline:</strong> February 26 to March 31, 2020 </span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Participant Eligibility: </strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Anyone buying AKASH DTH from our authorized retail outlets, direct sales and our website or e-commerce sites (e.g. Pickaboo, Daraz etc.) within Bangladesh, and activating within the campaign period (February 26 to March 31, 2020) are eligible for the campaign.</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Modality:</strong> </span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Step 1: Purchase-</strong>Customer will purchase AKASH connection and activate</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Step 2: Participate- </strong>Customers will type their subscriber ID in the instructed format <strong>(e.g. AKASHDTH SUBSCRIBER ID and send to 26969; e.g. Write AKASHDTH 40066460 and send to 26969)</strong>; In reply SMS customer will get a reply like “Thank you for your SMS”. </span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Step 3: Winner Announcement-</strong> Customer will get SMS and call from AKASH team (Winner will get information regarding the prize delivery date within 3 working days). (Names of 3 bat winners will be announced at the end of the campaign)</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Step 4: Prize Delivery- </strong>Jersey will be distributed among the winners at their respective registered addresses, and bat will be distributed at the end of the campaign at Beximco Communications Head Office (Level- 10, SAM Tower, Plot #4, Road #22, Gulshan- 1, Dhaka 1212, Bangladesh.)</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><u>Available Prizes:</u></strong><strong> </strong>New Official Bangladesh National Cricket Team Jersey <em>(For first 50 purchasers every day during the campaign period) and Team Signed Bats (for lucky 3 winners).</em></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">​<strong><u>TERMS & CONDITIONS</u></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Cricket Bat and Jersey Giveaway Campaign will remain active from February 26 to March 31, 2020. </span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">The participant must send the SMS as per specified format and from their registered mobile numbers only.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Winner names will be announced only after verification from AKASH team (Beximco Communications Ltd.), and it might take up to 3 working days to finalize and inform the winners. </span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">The purchaser must be Bangladeshi (Nationality) to be eligible for the campaign. </span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Anyone purchasing full AKASH connection (CPE) or only the STB from authorized retail outlets, e-commerce sites (e.g. Daraz, Pickaboo etc.) and AKASH website (Incl. through EMI, FnF Package and Corporate Offer) within Bangladesh, and activating during the campaign period are eligible for the campaign.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Retailer/Distributor of AKASH (Beximco Communications Ltd.) are not eligible to participate.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Employees of Beximco Communications Limited are not eligible, however their parents, siblings, spouses & children, friends are eligible to participate.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Existing AKASH DTH subscribers or inactive customer are not eligible to participate in the campaign, however they can participate through purchase of new AKASH connection during the campaign period (February 26 to March 31, 2020).</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Tentative date of prize delivery will be communicated to the respective winners over phone and SMS.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Daily jersey winners list will be finalized based on the participant’s earliest SMS sending time (Earliest first 50 SMS senders) and the 3 bat winners will be decided based on lucky draw after the end of the campaign from the total participant list.    </span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Only the valid registered subscriber will be entitled for the Prize, no one else can collect prize on behalf of the subscriber. </span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">People purchasing product before February 26, but activating during the campaign period (February 26 to March 31, 2020) are not be eligible for the campaign.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">AKASH (Beximco Communications Ltd.) assures its customers/subscribers that, there is no financial investment, deposit, security money required to enter Cricket Jersey Giveaway Campaign, all the customers/subscribers are requested to remain cautious for any such type of fraudulent offer. <em><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\">(Beximco Communications Ltd. won’t be responsible for any kind of personal or financial loss due to any fraudulent incident)</span></em></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">No transportation allowance or any form of allowance would be provided to winners when collecting the prize. </span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">By participating, the subscriber/purchaser agrees to be bound by these Terms & Conditions. Subscriber /purchaser must comply with these Terms & Conditions to be able to receive prize at the end of this campaign.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">AKASH (Beximco Communications Ltd.) reserves all the right to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">AKASH (Beximco Communications Ltd.) shall not be liable for any loss, damage or injury suffered or sustained (even if caused by negligence) as a result of accepting and/or using the prize, except for any liability which cannot be excluded by law.</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">​</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><u><span style=\"font-size:24.0pt\">FAQ</span></u></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"> </p>\n\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"Table\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; width:100.0%\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:1px solid black; height:75px; width:25%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">What is Cricket Bat and Jersey Giveaway Campaign?</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:1px solid black; height:75px; width:74%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Anyone buying AKASH DTH from our authorized retail outlets, direct sales and our website or e-commerce sites (e.g. Pickaboo, Daraz etc.) within Bangladesh, and activating within the campaign period (February 26 to March 31, 2020) are eligible for the campaign. Everyday first 50 purchasers will win exclusive official Bangladesh National Cricket Team Jersey which will be distributed among the winners at their respective registered addresses, and bat will be distributed at the end of the campaign at Beximco Communications Head Office (Level- 10, SAM Tower, Plot #4, Road #22, Gulshan- 1, Dhaka 1212, Bangladesh.)</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-botto