:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:46px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">BDT 128 to BDT 188</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:40px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">BDT 1251 to 5000</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:40px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">20%</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:40px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">It requires minimum recharge of BDT 1251 from both AKASH Lite & AKASH Standard Subscribers</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:40px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">BDT 250 BDT 1000</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"> </span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Terms & Conditions: </span></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">All AKASH Standard, AKASH Lite, and Inactive subscribers are considered eligible for this cashback campaign.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffff00\">After successful recharge, it can take up to 7 working days for the cashback amount to be disbursed in subscriber’s AKASH account.</span></span></span></strong></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Corporate entities which are our subscriber by contracts/corporate modalities/models are not eligible for this offer.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">A subscriber can recharge as many times as he or she wants. There is no restriction on the number of recharges a subscriber can make during the campaign period.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">A Subscriber can get a maximum of BDT 2200 during the campaign period. </span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Successive recharges will not be counted & treated as a single recharge. For instance, if a subscriber recharges BDT 800 and then BDT 800 again after that, he won’t be eligible for 20% cashback as his single recharge needs to exceed the minimum limit of BDT 1251 for eligibility of 20% cash back. Rather he or she will get 10% cashback for each of his BDT 800 recharges. </span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">The cashback amount can be used for consumption in packages, add on packs etc. permitted by AKASH.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">The validity of the cash back amount will not expire until its consumption. </span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">AKASH (Beximco Communications Ltd.) reserves all the right to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">During the campaign period, the usual offers of 6 month recharge & 12 month recharge (free subscription of 1 & 2 month) will not be valid for any subscribers.</span></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p> </p>\n', '1587028293-93601923.jpg', '1587028293-38826862.jpg', '', 'Promotional', 0, 0, 0, '2020-05-10 16:00:00', '2020-12-10 16:00:00', '2020-05-14 20:33:19', '2020-04-14 18:37:42', '');
