(16, 'Emergency Credit Offer', 'emergency-credit', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Considering the current pandemic and lockdown situation, AKASH is offering its subscribers with 5 days Emergency Credit Limit. This emergency credit facility is for those who are unable to recharge their account by themselves or find any recharge point. Credit amount will be automatically adjusted when customer recharge their AKASH account, without any interest charged.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\"> Offer Duration:</span></strong><span style=\"color:black\"> 10<sup>th</sup> April’20 to 7<sup>th</sup> May’20</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"> <strong>Terms and Condition</strong></span></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">To avail the offer, AKASH Subscriber needs to call the AKASH helpline (16442) during the offer period.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Customers who became inactive after 25<sup>th</sup> March, 2020 can avail this offer.</span></span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">AKASH (Beximco Communications Ltd.) reserves all the right to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</span></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">FAQ</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"> </span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">What is Emergency Credit facility?</span></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">The Emergency Credit facility is an additional 5 days credit facility for those who are unable to recharge their account because of the current situation. For these subscribers, AKASH is offering a balanced loan for 5 days’ time period. The balance credit under this loan will be debited from the user’s account as soon as they re-activate their service, without any interest being charged.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong> </strong></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Who will be eligible for this offer?</span></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Customers who became inactive after 25<sup>th</sup> March, 2020 are eligible for this offer.</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong> </strong></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">How to avail the Emergency Credit facility?</span></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">To avail the service, subscriber has to call AKASH helpline 16442</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong> </strong></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">After end of 5 days grace period will the customer be eligible to get another grace period?</span></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">No</span></span></span></p>\n', '1586868189-72071562.jpg', '1586868189-22899018.jpg', '', 'Promotional', 0, 0, 0, '2020-05-10 16:00:00', '2020-12-10 16:00:00', '2020-06-09 13:37:43', '2020-04-14 18:43:09', ''),
(17, 'Infotainment Pack 2', 'infotainment-2', '<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">AKASH has launched a new add on pack “Infotainment Pack 2”. This add on pack is available for both AKASH Lite & AKASH Standard Subscribers, consisting of 4 new channels. </span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Channel List:</span></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" style=\"height:117px; width:624px\" /> </span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Monthly Subscription of the pack:</span></strong><span style=\"color:black\"> BDT 21</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p> </p>\n', '1587472994-30725306.jpg', '1587472994-70825923.jpg', '', 'Product', 0, 0, 0, '2020-05-10 16:00:00', '2021-12-31 23:55:00', '2021-04-22 15:33:53', '2020-04-21 18:43:14', ''),
(18, 'AKASH Eid Campaign 2020', 'eid-cashback-2020', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">To celebrate the Eid with exciting quality TV viewing experiences of Eid programs, AKASH is bringing up to Tk. 400 cash-back on your new purchase of AKASH Connection. A person can get this cash-back offer by purchasing a new connection and paying one month’s subscription fee. </span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Campaign Duration:</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\"> May 12<sup>th</sup> to May 31<sup>st</sup>, 2020</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"> </span></span></p>\n\n<h1><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri Light\",sans-serif\"><strong>Terms & Conditions</strong></span></span></span></h1>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">All individuals (without any special contracts) are considered eligible for this cashback campaign while purchasing a new connection. </span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">If a customer after purchasing AKASH connection avails AKASH Standard package he will get BDT 400 cashback & if he avails AKASH Lite he will get BDT 250 Cashback in his AKASH account.</span></span></strong></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Customers buying multiple connections will be eligible for multiple cashback according to the packages he is adopting at the time of purchase/account creation.</span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Subscriber groups enjoying reduced product prices (STB/CPE) will not be eligible for this cashback offer. (i.e: Employee, Employee fnf, group employee, dealer, etc.)</span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Corporate entities which are our subscriber by contracts/ are in invoicing relations or in rental modalities/models are not eligible for this offer.</span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">To be eligible for cashback, the customer needs to buy new connection & recharge at least 1 month’s equivalent subscription amount after his/her purchase & within the campaign period.</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\"> However, as customer buying on last day of campaign may need time for set-up and activation, therefore he/she can recharge up to the 7<sup>th</sup> of June to get the offer.</span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Those who will do recharge will not get additional cashback on recharge under our Boishakhi Cash Back Campaign.</span></span></strong></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">People purchasing product before 12<sup>th</sup> May 2020, but activating during the campaign period (12<sup>th</sup> May to 31<sup>st</sup> May, 2020) are not be eligible for the campaign.</span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">The cashback amount can be used for consumption in packages, add on packs, etc. permitted by AKASH.</span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">The validity of the cashback amount will expire within 3 months after the disbursement date of Cashback in case of one month\'s recharge. The expiration date will be counted from the end of bonus month in case of multiple months\' payment offer. For example, if anyone pays 6 months\' subscription fee, he will get 1 month free. In that case, the expiration date will be counted from the end of 7th month for 1 additional month. In total, it will be 8 months in a row. In the similar way, it will be 15 months\' active account, if anyone purchase for 12 months (12+2+1).</span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">AKASH (Beximco Communications Ltd.) assures its customers/subscribers that, there is no financial investment, deposit, security money required to enter AKASH Eid Campaign, all the customers/subscribers are requested to remain cautious for any such type of fraudulent offer. <em>(Beximco Communications Ltd. won’t be responsible for any kind of personal or financial loss due to any fraudulent incident)</em></span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">By participating, the subscriber/ purchaser agrees to be bound by these Terms & Conditions. Subscriber /purchaser must comply with these Terms & Conditions to be able to receive the cashback from this campaign. </span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">AKASH (Beximco Communications Ltd.) reserves all the right to change, extend, and cancel the offer at any time.</span></span></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', '1589234679-61084273.jpg', '1589234679-26421384.jpg', '', 'Promotional', 0, 0, 0, '2020-05-10 16:00:00', '2020-12-10 16:00:00', '2020-06-01 01:15:51', '2020-05-12 04:04:39', '');
INSERT INTO `offers` (`id`, `name`, `slug`, `description`, `thumb_image`, `banner_image`, `app_image`, `tags`, `show_in_app`, `show_buy_btn`, `state`, `start_time`, `end_time`, `updatedOn`, `createdOn`, `uda`) VALUES
(19, 'Online Cashback Campaign', 'online-cashback', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">Now it’s easier than ever to buy a new AKASH Connection from the comfort of your own home! Enjoy up to <strong>BDT 900 Cashback</strong>. Our team of expert professional installers will install AKASH in your home following proper health safety guidelines.</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">So buy AKASH from online and enjoy cashback on top of existing campaigns. </span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">Stay Home and Enjoy AKASH !!!</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Campaign Period: </span></strong><span style=\"color:black\">15<sup>th</sup> May 2020 – 31<sup>st</sup> May 2020 </span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Campaign Eligibility: </span></strong><span style=\"color:black\">Customers, purchasing a new AKASH connection only through AKASH website or partner online portal (Daraz, Priyoshop.com, Easyhaat) either STB or CPE and recharging for a minimum of 1 month (Either TK. 399 for AKASH Standard or TK. 249 for AKASH Lite) during the campaign period (15<sup>th</sup> May to 31<sup>st</sup> May) will be entitled for the cashback reward (On top of/in addition to the cashback amount of the Eid Cashback Campaign). </span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"> </span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Terms and Conditions</span></strong></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:30px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Symbol\"><span style=\"color:black\">·</span></span>         <span style=\"color:black\">The customer purchasing new AKASH connection (STB or Full CPE) and who’s activating AKASH Standard pack will receive TK. 500 cashback and who’s activating AKASH Lite will receive TK. 250 cashback in his AKASH account on top of/in addition to the cashback amount of the Eid Cashback Campaign which is BDT 400 for standard user and BDT 250 for Lite user. So the total cashback amount for AKASH Standard user is <strong>(BDT 500 + BDT 400 = BDT 900)</strong> and AKASH Lite user is <strong>(BDT 250</strong> + <strong>BDT 250 = BDT 500).</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:30px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Symbol\"><span style=\"color:black\">·</span></span>         <span style=\"color:black\">After a successful recharge, it can take up to 12 working days for the cashback amount to be disbursed in the subscriber’s AKASH account.</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:30px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Symbol\"><span style=\"color:black\">·</span></span>         <span style=\"color:black\">Customers buying multiple connections will be eligible for multiple cashbacks according to their activated respective packages after purchase/account creation. </span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:30px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Symbol\"><span style=\"color:black\">·</span></span>         <span style=\"color:black\">Subscriber/Customer groups already enjoying reduced product price (STB/CPE) or subscription fee will not be eligible for this cashback offer. <em>(i.e: Employee, employee fnf, group employee, dealer, etc.) </em></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:30px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Symbol\"><span style=\"color:black\">·</span></span>         <span style=\"color:black\">Corporate entities which are our subscriber by contracts/ are in invoicing relations or in rental modalities/models are not eligible for this offer. </span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:30px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Symbol\"><span style=\"color:black\">·</span></span>         <span style=\"color:black\">To be eligible for cashback, the customer will need to buy new connection & recharge at least 1 month’s equivalent subscription amount after his/her purchase & within the campaign period. However, as customer buying on the last day of the campaign may need time for set-up and activation, therefore he/she can recharge up to 7<sup>th</sup> of June to get the offer. </span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:30px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Symbol\"><span style=\"color:black\">·</span></span>         <span style=\"color:black\">The cashback amount can be used for consumption in packages, add on packs etc. permitted by AKASH.</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:30px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Symbol\"><span style=\"color:black\">·</span></span>         <span style=\"color:black\">The validity of the cashback amount will expire within 3 months after the disbursement date of Cashback. The expiration date will be counted from the end of the bonus month in case of multiple months\' payment offer. For example, if anyone pays 6 months\' subscription fee, he will get 1 month free. In that case, the expiration date will be counted from the end of 7th month for 1 additional month. In total, it will be 8 months in a row. Similarly, it will be 15 months\' active account, if anyone purchase for 12 months (12+2+1). </span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:30px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Symbol\"><span style=\"color:black\">·</span></span>         <span style=\"color:black\">AKASH (Beximco Communications Ltd.) assures its customers/subscribers that, there is no financial investment, deposit, security money required to enter Online Cashback Campaign, all the customers/subscribers are requested to remain cautious for any such type of fraudulent offer. (Beximco Communications Ltd. won’t be responsible for any kind of personal or financial loss due to any fraudulent incident)</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:30px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Symbol\"><span style=\"color:black\">·</span></span>         <span style=\"color:black\">By participating, the subscriber/ purchaser agrees to be bound by these Terms & Conditions. Subscriber /purchaser must comply with these Terms & Conditions to be able to receive the cashback from this campaign.</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:30px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Symbol\"><span style=\"color:black\">·</span></span>         <span style=\"color:black\">AKASH (Beximco Communications Ltd.) reserves all the right to change, extend, and cancel the offer at any time.</span></span></p>\n', '1589477970-94498914.jpg', '1589477970-11389950.jpg', '', 'Promotional', 0, 0, 0, '2020-05-14 23:55:12', '2020-05-31 23:55:12', '2020-06-01 01:16:10', '2020-05-14 23:39:30', ''),
(20, 'Vision Cashback Campaign June’20', 'vision-cashback-june20', '<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">Buy new AKASH connection (STB/CPE) from Vision (Both Vision online platform and their physical outlets- Vision Emporium) during June 2020 and recharge for the first month to get up to Tk. 400 cashback in your Akash account.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">If the customer activates AKASH Standard pack through recharge (Minimum recharge amount TK 399) he/she will receive TK 400 cashback and if activates AKASH Lite (Minimum recharge amount TK 249), he/she will receive TK 250 cashback in their respective AKASH account.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><strong>Campaign Period: </strong>12 June 2020 – 24 June 2020</span></p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><strong><u><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">FAQ</span></u></strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><strong>What is this CASHBACK Campaign? / How to participate in this Campaign?</strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><strong>Ans:</strong> Customers purchasing from Vision (Both Vision online platform and their physical outlets- Vision Emporium) activating AKASH Standard pack will receive TK. 400 cashback and who’s activating AKASH Lite will receive TK. 250 cashback in his AKASH account within 12 working days.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><strong>How long is the duration of this campaign?</strong>        </span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><strong>Ans:</strong> For 13 days (12th June 2020 – 24th June 2020)</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><strong>How much cash-back in total can I get from this particular campaign?    </strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><strong>Ans:</strong> Anyone customer purchasing from Vision (Both Vision online platform and their physical outlets- Vision Emporium) activating AKASH Standard pack will receive TK. 400 cashback and who’s activating AKASH Lite will receive TK. 250 cashback in his AKASH account within 12 working days.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><strong>If I purchase only STB, will I be eligible for the Cashback?</strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><strong>Ans:</strong> Yes! If you purchase the full AKASH connection or only the STB through the specified partner platforms or AKASH website and recharge minimum for the first month (AKASH Standard or AKASH Lite).</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><strong>I\'m a current subscriber of AKASH. Am I eligible for the cashback?</strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><strong>Ans:</strong> No, only subscribers purchasing new AKASH CPE or the STB from 12th June 2020 – 24th June 2020 through the specified platforms and recharging for a minimum for a month are eligible for the cashback. If you have purchased AKASH before 12th June 2020 you’re not eligible; however, you can still participate in the campaign by buying additional new connections during the specified campaign period.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><strong>Do I need to recharge after activating my connection to participate in this campaign?</strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><strong>Ans:</strong> Yes, you need to recharge. After purchasing the CPE or the STB, you must recharge a minimum for 1 month to be eligible for the cashback. (Minimum recharge amount TK. 399 for AKASH Standard pack or TK. 249 for AKASH Lite pack)</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><strong>I bought AKASH Connection- CPE/STB before 12th June 2020 but my installation has been completed on or after 24th June 2020; am I eligible for the campaign?</strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><strong>Ans:</strong> No, only customers purchasing new connections (STB or CPE) and recharging within the specified campaign period are eligible. If you have purchased AKASH before 12th June 2020, you can still participate in the campaign by buying additional connections or STBs during the specified campaign period. However, if you purchase within the campaign period (12th June 2020 – 24th June 2020) but your installation was done after the campaign period, you will get up to 2nd July 2020 to recharge and get the cashback. offer. (NOTE: Please be informed that you can recharge right after your subscription ID is being created)</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><strong>I\'m an employee of AKASH/Beximco Communications Limited. Will I be eligible for the cashback?</strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><strong>Ans:</strong> Subscriber/Customer groups already enjoying reduced product prices (STB/CPE) will not be eligible for this cashback offer. (i.e: Employee, employee fnf, group employee, dealer, etc.). However, anyone purchasing a new connection (STB/CPE) online (through specified platforms) connection as a regular customer will be eligible for the cashback.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><strong>I’m an employee of the Beximco Group. Am I eligible?          </strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">No, Subscriber/Customer groups already enjoying reduced product price (STB/CPE) will not be eligible for this cashback offer. (i.e: Employee, employee fnf, group employee, dealer, etc.) However, anyone purchasing a new connection (STB/CPE) through specified platforms connection as a regular customer at a regular price will be eligible for the cashback.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><strong>I’m a new subscriber of AKASH; I got a one-month free subscription through referral program/other programs/special offers. Do I need to recharge to participate in this campaign?       </strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">Yes, your purchasing date must be within the campaign period (12th June 2020 – 24th June 2020) and you’ll have to recharge. You must recharge a minimum for 1 month to be eligible for the cashback. (Minimum recharge amount TK. 399 for AKASH Standard pack or TK. 249 for AKASH Lite pack) But don’t worry! Your free subscriptions will remain valid as well!</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><strong>If I purchase through EMI or Online within 12th June 2020 – 24th June 2020, will I be eligible?  </strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">Yes! You will be eligible if you purchase a new connection (STB or CPE) through EMI and recharge a minimum for 1 month.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><strong>I am an existing retailer/Distributor of AKASH. Am I eligible for this campaign?       </strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">No, you cannot participate in the campaign. This campaign is only for new AKASH Subscribers only excluding Subscriber/Customer groups already enjoying reduced product price (STB/CPE) or subscription fees (i.e: Employee, employee fnf, group employee, dealer, corporate individuals, etc.) However, anyone purchasing a new connection (STB/CPE) online (through specified platforms) connection as a regular customer will be eligible for the cashback.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><strong>I purchased an AKASH connection from 15th June 2020 – 24th June 2020 with a corporate offer. Am I eligible? </strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">No. Subscriber/Customer groups already enjoying reduced product price (STB/CPE) will not be eligible for this cashback offer. (i.e: Employee, employee fnf, group employee, dealer, corporate individuals, etc.) However, anyone purchasing a new connection (STB/CPE) online (through specified platforms) connection as a regular customer will be eligible for the cashback.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><strong>I purchased the AKASH CPE/STB & activated within 12th June 2020 – 24th June 2020 If I recharge for 6 months or 12 months, am I eligible?</strong> </span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">Yes, you’ll be eligible only If you recharge for a minimum of 1 month after the purchase (Minimum recharge amount TK. 399 for AKASH Standard pack or TK. 249 for AKASH Lite pack).</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><strong>I purchased an AKASH connection within 12th June 2020 – 24th June 2020 through employee fnf offer. Am I eligible to participate?</strong>      </span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">No. Subscriber/Customer groups already enjoying reduced product price (STB/CPE) will not be eligible for this cashback offer. (i.e: Employee, employee fnf, group employee, dealer, corporate individuals, etc.) However, anyone purchasing a new connection (STB/CPE) through specified platforms a regular customer at a regular price will be eligible for the cashback.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><strong>What will be the CPE Price/STB Price/Package price during the campaign?</strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">AKASH Connection is available at only TK. 5499 & only STB is available at TK. 3199 now! These prices will also remain valid during the campaign period. And the subscription fees for the AKASH Standard package and AKASH Lite package are TK. 399 and TK. 249 respectively.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><strong>Will we be still able to enjoy the default-free subscription period? </strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">Yes, new subscribers during the campaign period will be eligible for the default 5-day free subscription period.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><strong>How long will it take to receive the cashback amount?</strong> </span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">It might take up to 12 (Maximum) working days from the day of recharge to receive the cashback amount in the customer’s respective AKASH account.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><strong>Can I get the cashback amount in the form of actual cash instead of the AKASH account recharge?</strong> </span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">No, it’s only possible to receive the amount through the AKASH account and can be used to buy subscriptions and add-on packs.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><strong>How can I check my existing AKASH account balance?   </strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">Call our call center number 16442 or through SMS (Write AKASHSUB ID send to 26969</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><strong>What is the validity of the cash-back amount?</strong>  </span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">The cash-back amount will remain valid for three (3) months from the day of recharge. The expiration date will be counted from the end of the bonus month in case of multiple months\' payment offer. For example, if anyone pays 6 months\' subscription fee, he will get 1 month free. In that case, the expiration date will be counted from the end of the 7th month for 1 additional month. In total, it will be 8 months in a row. Similarly, it will be 15 months\' active account, if anyone purchases for 12 months (12+2+1).</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><strong>What can I do with the cash-back amount?</strong>        </span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">Pay monthly subscription and subscribe to add-on packs only. No device can be purchased with that amount.</span></p>\n', '1591921946-60222299.png', '1591921946-87385639.png', '', 'Promotional', 0, 0, 0, '2020-06-12 06:30:37', '2020-06-30 23:55:37', '2020-06-28 01:03:21', '2020-06-12 06:32:26', ''),
