/span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:140px; width:77%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Not at all! In fact, you should recharge as fast you can after you purchase the connection! Your 5 day free subscription period won&#39;t be hampered at all! Your wallet will be recharged at the time of recharge and the balance will be deducted after the expiry of the 5 day free subscription period.</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:80px; width:23%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">What are the prizes in the weekly contest?</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:80px; width:77%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">For each week, 20 successful participants will be declared as winners based on their response time after hearing the question. Therefore, the first 20 participants who will successfully answer the quiz question will be eligible for the weekly prizes. The prizes include 55&rsquo;&rsquo;, 43&#39;&#39; &amp; 32&#39;&#39; inch TVs of LG, Samsung &amp; Walton!</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:40px; width:23%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">What will be the brand of TVs for the weekly prizes?</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:40px; width:77%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">LG, Samsung and Walton </span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:60px; width:23%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">How will the winners know that they have won the prizes?</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:60px; width:77%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">The names of the weekly contest winners will be published on our Facebook page (www.facebook.com/akashdthbangladesh) on weekly basis. Also, all winners will get SMS to their registered mobile number &amp; we&#39;ll also call them to inform them about further details of the prizes.</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:80px; width:23%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">How will I collect the prizes?</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:80px; width:77%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">The winners will get a call from us regarding further details of the prizes. In short, weekly TV winners will need to come physically to our regional offices; weekly TV winners from Dhaka will need to visit AKASH headquarter. The winners will need to the visit the designated collection point as mentioned at the pre-specified time by AKASH. The addresses of the prize collection points will be communicated to winners when we call them. </span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:40px; width:23%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Do I need to come physically to collect the prizes?</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:40px; width:77%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Only the valid registered subscriber will be entitled for the Prize, no one else can collect prize on behalf of the subscriber </span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:40px; width:23%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">What do I need to bring to collect prizes?</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:40px; width:77%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">NID copy and winning SMS with the Customer ID carrying the same RMN need to be shown. Details will be communicated to the winners at the time we call the winners.</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:60px; width:23%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">After I answer the quiz question, how long will it take to know I have won?</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:60px; width:77%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">The names of the weekly contest winners will be published on our Facebook page (www.facebook.com/akashdthbangladesh) on weekly basis.&nbsp; Also, all winners will get SMS to their registered mobile number &amp; we&#39;ll also call them to inform them about further details of the prizes.</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:40px; width:23%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Will I get SMS/any notification if I don&#39;t win any prizes?</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:40px; width:77%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">No, only the winners will be notified.</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:80px; width:23%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Will the winners get any transportation allowance for visiting the designated point to collect the prizes?</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:80px; width:77%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">No transportation allowance would be provided to winners when collecting the prize</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:60px; width:23%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Can I get the equivalent cash amount for the prize won?</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:60px; width:77%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Prizes won are not transferable and cannot be combined with any other prize or any other offer or discounts or promotions offered by AKASH. Only in the events of exhaustion of existing stock or due to political instability, natural calamities, in such cases prizes will be replaced by other available prizes of same monetary value.</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n', '1598972893-56692918.jpg', '1598972893-96217261.jpg', '', 'Offer', 0, 0, 1, '2020-08-31 23:55:41', '2020-09-30 23:55:41', '2020-09-02 17:34:01', '2020-08-31 14:29:39', '');
