(33, 'AKASH - Walton Television Joint Campaign', 'walton-tv', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\">This campaign is designed to give the WALTON TV buyers a 10% cashback using coupon if they purchase AKASH Connection, activates and recharges for it. A customer who buys WALTON TV would get the 10% cashback coupon from Walton store. The customer has to call our call center to purchase AKASH connection or he/she can buy AKASH connection from our retail stores or online. Upon buying, activating AKASH connection and recharging for a month, the customer has to call at our call center to place a request for the 10% cashback. Our call center agent will verify the subscriber information and eligibility and forward the request to revenue assurance team who will further provide the cashback in the subscribers AKASH account. 10% cashback amount would be on the MRP of AKASH basic and regular box. The amount of the cashback would be BDT 400 or 450 depending on the respective product purchased.  </span></span></span></p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\">Campaign Timeline:</span></strong><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"> </span><strong><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"> </span></strong><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\">20/12/2020 – 31/01/2021  </span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\">Terms & Conditions </span></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<ol>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\">Customers have to collect the coupon from Walton Showroom and would get it only if they buy Walton TV. </span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\">Customers can buy AKASH connection from our / partner stores, online or AKASH call center.  </span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\">One customer can avail one campaign offer at a time.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\">To avail the 10% cashback customers, have to activate the connection, recharge for a month and place the request to our call with proper customer verification.  </span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\">It would take 10 working days for the customers to receive the cashback amount in their AKASH account.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\">To avail this offer customer has to purchase the AKASH connection by 31</span><sup><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\">st</span></sup><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"> January 2021 and the coupon would be valid till 7</span><sup><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\">th</span></sup><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"> February 2021. The recharge has to be done within 7</span><sup><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\">th</span></sup><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"> February to avail the cashback. </span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=