(34, '100% Addon Cashback Campaign', 'addon-cashback', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">To give the customers a delight in content viewership, AKASH brings an offer for its five available addon packs: Entertainment, Infotainment, Sports, Kids and Infotainment pack 2. Customers will get 100% cashback on any New Addon package activation during the campaign. </span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Price of different Addon packs for one month:</span></span></span></p>\n\n<ol>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Entertainment Addon: BDT 75.00</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Sports Addon: BDT 71.00</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Kids Addon: BDT 30.00</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Infotainment Addon: BDT 45.00</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Infotainment Pack 2: BDT 21.00</span></span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Upon successful activation of new addon, customers will get cashback equal to one-month recharge price of that addon.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Campaign Duration:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\"> 25 Dec 2020 – 10 Jan 2021 (17 days)</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Terms and Conditions:</span></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">All the customers will be eligible for this offer if they have not already taken all possible addons.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Addons should be newly onboarded and activated during the campaign period to avail this offer.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Recharging any INACTIVE addons will not be included in this offer.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">If anyone already has one addon, he can take other addons to avail this offer. </span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">If anyone already has all the possible addons onboarded, he will not be included in the offer.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">If a customer is in 6 months or 12 months billing cycle and add any new addon, he/she will get the cashback equal to one-month recharge of the addon.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Cashbacks will be given to customer’s Akash Wallet within 15 January 2021</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">AKASH reserves all rights to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</span></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">FAQ:</span></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q1. Am I eligible for this campaign?</span></span></span></strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: If you already haven’t taken all the possible addons (Infotainment pack 2 for Akash Standard and All 5 addons for Akash Lite), you are Eligible.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q2. What is the offer?</span></span></span></strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: by Activating any new Addon during the campaign, you will get 100% cashback on one-month price of that addon.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q3. How can I activate any new addon?</span></span></span></strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: by calling 16442, and through Akash Self-care. (FYI: Not yet) </span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q4. How will I get the cashback?</span></span></span></strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: Cashback will be given in your Akash Wallet within 15 January 2021.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q5. I already have Entertainment Addon (or any other), but I didn’t recharge it. Will I get the cashback if I recharge now?</span></span></span></strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: No. But you can get the cashback if you take any other cashback (Like Sports or Kids etc)</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q6. I am currently availing 1-month free offer for 6 months recharge, how can I get this offer?</span></span></span></strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: You need to recharge for 6 months for an Addon to activate it. Then you will get the cashback equal to 1-month recharge of your addon. In your case, it won’t be 100% cashback.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q7. What will be the cashback amounts?</span></span></span></strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: For Entertainment Addon: BDT 75.00</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Infotainment Addon: BDT 45.00</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Sports Addon: BDT 71.00</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Kids Addon: BDT 30.00</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Infotainment pack 2: BDT 21.00</span></span></span></p>\n', '1608887800-26104423.jpg', '1608887801-13933462.jpg', '', 'Offer', 0, 0, 1, '2020-12-25 11:00:53', '2021-01-10 23:55:53', '2020-12-25 15:16:41', '2020-12-24 21:39:32', ''),
(35, 'Year-end Recharge Campaign', 'year-end-recharge', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">2020 is about to end. Hoping for the end of COVID-19 driven sorrow and grief of 2020, Akash brings Year-end recharge blast for its customers. Any customer recharging BDT 500 or more within the campaign period will get a fixed cashback of BDT 50 in his Akash Wallet. A customer can avail this offer as many times as he/she wants during campaign period.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Campaign Duration:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\"> 27 December 2020 to 31 December 2020 (5 days)</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Terms & Conditions:</span></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<ol>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">All the cashbacks will be given to customer’s Akash account at once within 6 January 2021.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">All the permitted subscribers of AKASH STANDARD and AKASH LITE are eligible for this campaign.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">A subscriber can recharge as many times as he wants. There’s no restriction on the number of recharges a subscriber can make during the campaign period. Every time he can avail this offer.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Successive recharges will NOT be counted & treated as a single recharge. For instance, if a subscriber recharges BDT 400 and then BDT 100, he will not get the cashback. Customer needs to recharge BDT 500 or more at a single recharge.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">The cashback amount can be used for consumption in packages, add on packs etc. permitted by AKASH.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">The validity of the cash back amount will not expire until its consumption. </span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">VIP, VVIP and Engineering class of customers who don’t have to recharge are excluded from the offer.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">AKASH reserves all rights to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Campaign FAQs:</span></strong></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q1. How can I avail 50-taka cashback offer?</span></span></span></strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: By recharging BDT 500 or more to your Akash account at a single recharge within 27 Dec 2020 to 31 Dec 2020.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q2. Where will the customer get this cashback?</span></span></span></strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: Cashback will be given to your Akash wallet.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q3. When I can avail this offer?</span></span></span></strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: You can avail this offer by recharging BDT 500 or more to your Akash account at a single recharge withi<em>n 27 Dec 2020 to 31 Dec 2020.</em></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q4. When will I get the cashback?</span></span></span></strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: All the cashbacks will be given to your Akash Wallet within 6 January 2021. You will get an SMS confirmation after that.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q5. Why am I getting this cashback?</span></span></span></strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: This is a year-end recharge delight for you as a valued customer of Akash.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q6. Can I avail this offer more than once?</span></span></span></strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: Yes, you can avail this offer as many times as you want within the campaign period by recharging 500 taka or more every time.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q7. During campaign, if I recharge fractionally (not at a time) to make it BDT 500, will I get the cashback?</span></span></span></strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: Fractional recharges will NOT be counted & treated as a single recharge. For instance, if you recharge BDT 400 and then BDT 100, you will not get the cashback. You need to recharge BDT 500 or more at a single recharge to get the cashback.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q8. What if I recharge more than 500- taka?</span></span></span></strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: Even if you recharge 50,000-taka in a single recharge, you will only get 50-taka cashback. But if you recharge 500 taka 100 times, you will get 50-taka for every recharge i.e. 50x100 = 5,000 taka.</span></span></span></p>\n', '1608996586-36327174.jpg', '1608996586-81655780.jpg', '', 'Offer', 0, 0, 1, '2020-12-26 23:55:00', '2020-12-31 23:55:00', '2021-01-01 15:03:08', '2020-12-26 21:29:46', '');
