(36, '100% Cashback on One-Month Recharge (Online Purchase Only)', 'new-connection-recharge-cashback', '<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Now buying AKASH is more rewarding with 100% Cashback on one-month recharge. A customer who buys AKASH connection from AKASH website can avail and enjoy the cashback.&nbsp; Once the connection is activated, customer has to make the recharge for minimum one month and would get the cashback in his or her AKASH account with 10 working days of the recharge date. </span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Campaign Timeline: 05-19 February 2021</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Terms and Conditions:</span></span></p>\n\n<ol>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">Customers has to buy AKASH connection from our website only within the campaign period. </span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">To avail the 100% cashback, customers have to activate the connection, recharge for a minimum one month and get the cashback within 10 working days from the day recharge. </span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">It would take 10 working days for the customers to receive the cashback amount in their AKASH account.</span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">To avail this offer customer has to purchase the AKASH connection within the campaign period (19<sup>th</sup> February 2021) and the recharge and installation has to made no later than 26th&nbsp;February 2021. The recharge and installation has to be done within 26th&nbsp;February 2021 to avail the cashback. </span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">Recharge and installation after 26th&nbsp;February 2021 would not be considered for cashback.</span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">Any amount of cashback given under this campaign cannot be uncashed or transferred by the beneficiary. </span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">AKASH reserves all the right to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">The customer who will avail this campaign will be eligible for Jersey Campaign, purchase has to be made by 15<sup>th</sup> February 2021. </span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">The customers who will avail AKASH-AMEX campaign would not be eligible for this campaign.&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"Table\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; width:100.0%\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"background-color:#d9d9d9; border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:none; border-top:1px solid black; height:33px; vertical-align:bottom; width:3%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"background-color:#d9d9d9; border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:1px solid black; height:33px; vertical-align:top; width:37%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">FAQ</span></span></strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"background-color:#d9d9d9; border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:1px solid black; height:33px; vertical-align:top; width:59%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">Answers </span></span></strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:73px; vertical-align:top; width:3%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:right\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">1</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:73px; vertical-align:top; width:37%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">What is 100% Cashback Campaign on online purchase?</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:73px; vertical-align:top; width:59%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">A customer who buys AKASH connection from AKASH website within the campaign period. After activating the connection and recharging for at least one month. If the customer is eligible, he/she would get the cashback amount in his AKASH account within 10 working days from the day of recharge. </span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:34px; vertical-align:top; width:3%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:right\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">2</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:34px; vertical-align:top; width:37%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">How long is the duration of this 100% Cashback Campaign on online purchase??</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:34px; vertical-align:top; width:59%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">05-19 February 2021</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:131px; vertical-align:top; width:3%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:right\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">3</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:131px; v