(37, '200 Taka Cashback!', '200-taka-cashback', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\">AKASH is always working on bringing new offers for its customers. Once new AKASH connections created and activated, customer has to make the recharge for minimum one month and his or her account will be credited with the cashback amount by 11<sup>th</sup> of February 2021.&nbsp;The amount of the cashback is fixed BDT 200 and will not be dependent on the price of subscription of the fist package taken. </span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\">Campaign Timeline:</span></strong> <strong>&nbsp;</strong><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\">25/01/2021 &ndash; 31/01/2021 </span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\">Terms &amp; Conditions&nbsp;</span></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<ol>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><a name=\"_Hlk61447221\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\">Customers can buy AKASH connection from retail stores,&nbsp;online and call center within 25-31 January 2021</span></a></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\">To avail the BDT 200 cashback, customers have to activate the connection, recharge for a month. </span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\">Customers would receive the cashback amount in their AKASH account on 11<sup>th</sup> February 2021.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=