(39, 'Jersey Campaign Feb’21', 'jersey-feb-21', '<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">AKASH continuously thrives to make our customers AKASH purchase more rewarding, in the month of February buy a new connection and participate in the campaign quiz to win a Bangladesh National Cricket Team Jersey for free!</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Participant Eligibility Criteria: </span></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Anyone buying AKASH DTH from our authorized retail outlets, direct sales, online &amp; call center, and activating &amp; recharging a minimum one month of BDT 399/249 would get a chance to win a Bangladesh National Cricket Team jersey (replica) by participating in a quiz.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Campaign Timeline:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"> 1<sup> </sup>-15 February 2021 </span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Modality:</span></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><u><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Contest: </span></u><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">All new subscribers who will buy a new AKASH* DTH connection from 1-5 Feb&rsquo;21 and recharge a minimum of BDT 399/249 for such connection by 8<sup>th</sup> Feb&rsquo;21 will be eligible for the game on 9<sup>th</sup> Feb&rsquo;21. Onwards the customers who will buy a new AKASH DTH connection from 6-10 Feb&rsquo;21 and recharge a minimum of BDT 399/249 for such connection by 13<sup>th</sup> Feb&rsquo;21 will be eligible for the game on 14<sup>th</sup> Feb&rsquo;21. Furthermore, the customers who will buy a new AKASH DTH connection from 11-15 Feb&rsquo;21 and recharge a minimum of BDT 399/249 for such connection by 21<sup>st</sup> Feb&rsquo;21 will be eligible for the game on 22<sup>nd</sup> Feb&rsquo;21. </span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Customers need to correctly answer a question through a quiz to be conducted via automated Interactive voice response (IVR) and first 700 to correctly answer in the shortest possible time will be selected as the winner on the basis of fastest finger first. The winner and participant of a single contest will not be eligible to participate in the quiz for upcoming week &nbsp;of the month of February unless the winner and/or participant buys a new AKASH DTH connection in the remaining time. </span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">SMS containing a toll-free number for eligible participants to callback would be sent on February 9<sup>th</sup>, February 14<sup>th</sup> and February 22<sup>nd</sup>, eligible participants would have to give a missed call in the provided number and answer a single question and winner would be selected on Fastest Finger First basis. Participants would be allowed a maximum of 24 hours to participate from time of eligibility confirmation SMS sent to provide their answer. The winners will get their Jersey (replica) hand delivered via courier service. </span></span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><u><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">RULES</span></u></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<ol>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">New subscriber must activate and recharge for 1-month subscription to be eligible for the JERSEY CAMPAIGN FEB&rsquo;21, eligible participants will get a SMS, they have to give a &lsquo;missed call&rsquo; on the provided number to take part in the quiz. </span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">The quiz will be based on Interactive voice response (IVR) and the participant needs follow the instructions and respond accordingly.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">There will be 1 question for the quiz contest.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Participants must participate in the contest within the next 24 hours from the time they received the eligibility confirmation SMS. Late response will result in disqualification. &nbsp;</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Top 700 winners will be selected on every contest. Winners will get a winning con