(50, 'AKASH -SAMSUNG DOUBLE BONANZA', 'akash-samsung-double-bonanza', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">This joint campaign has been designed to make the AKASH purchase more rewarding for a SAMSUNG TV customer. This offer has double benefit where customers can enjoy a discounted price of AKASH DTH when purchase in bundle with SAMSUNG TV and on top there would be 100% Cashback on first month recharge. </span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">&nbsp;A customer who buys AKASH connection from selected SAMSUNG&rsquo;s partner outlet of Fair Electronics and Electra International will enjoy up to 25% discount on AKASH DTH when bought in bundle with selective UHD and QLED SAMSUNG TV.&nbsp; Once the connection is activated, customer has to make the recharge for minimum one month 249 / 399 or more (at one transaction) and get a 100% cashback up to BDT 1,200. </span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Campaign Timeline:</strong> <strong>&nbsp;</strong>1st&nbsp;April-30th&nbsp;May&rsquo;2021</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Terms &amp; Conditions&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<ol>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Customers can buy AKASH connection from selected partners outlet of Fair Electronics and Electra International by 30th&nbsp;May&rsquo;2021</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">To avail the 100% cashback, customers have to activate the connection, recharge for a month 249/399 or more at one transaction and get a 100% cashback up to BDT 1,200.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">It would take 10 working days for the customers to receive the cashback amount in their AKASH account from the recharge date.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">To avail this offer customer has to purchase the AKASH connection within the campaign period (1st&nbsp;April-30th&nbsp;May&rsquo;2021). The installation and recharge have to be done within 7th June 2021 to avail the cashback.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">After 7th June the recharge would be considered invalid, and no cashback request can be placed in reference to the same. </span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Any amount of cashback given under this campaign cannot be uncashed or transferred by the beneficiary. And it&rsquo;s not related to any other campaign or discount of AKASH. </span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">AKASH reserves all the right to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">One customer can avail one offer at a time. </span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">The Cashback amount will be given in customers AKASH account and they would be notified by an SMS.</span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">List of selected partners outlet of Fair Electronics and Electra Inter