"font-family:Kalpurush\">১৩</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Kalpurush\">.</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Kalpurush\"> ছবিতে আকাশ-এর যে-কোনো প্রোডাক্ট স্পষ্টভাবে থাকতে হবে। যেমন</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Kalpurush\">: ডিশ বা সেট-টপ বক্স বা রিমোট</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Kalpurush\">।</span></span> </span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Kalpurush\">১৪</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Kalpurush\">. </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Kalpurush\">ফেক</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Kalpurush\">আইডি</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Kalpurush\">থেকে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Kalpurush\">ছবি</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Kalpurush\">আপলোড</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Kalpurush\">করা</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Kalpurush\">হলে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Kalpurush\">তার</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Kalpurush\">অংশগ্রহণ</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Kalpurush\">বাতিল</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Kalpurush\">বলে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Kalpurush\">গণ্য</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Kalpurush\">হবে</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-fa