size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">All the customers will be eligible for this offer if they have not already taken all possible add-ons.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Add-ons should be newly onboarded and activated during the campaign period to avail this offer.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Recharging any INACTIVE add-ons will not be included in this offer.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">If anyone already has one add on, he can take other add-ons to avail this offer. </span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">If anyone already has all the possible add-ons onboarded, he will NOT be included in the offer.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">If a customer is in 6 months (1-month free) or 12 months (2-month free) billing cycle and add an addon pack, he/she will get the cashback equal to one-month recharge of the addon. In that case, it won’t be 100% cashback.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Cashbacks will be given to customer’s AKASH Account within 05 August 2021.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Customer will NOT get any cashback if he removes the add on pack before the campaign ends.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">AKASH reserves all rights to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</span></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">FAQ:</span></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q1. Am I eligible for this campaign?</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: If you already haven’t taken all the possible add-ons (Infotainment pack 2 for AKASH Standard, all add-ons except Entertainment for AKASH Lite Plus, and All 5 addons for AKASH Lite), you are Eligible.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q2. What is the offer?</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: By Activating and recharging any new Add on pack during the campaign, you will get 100% cashback on one-month price of that addon.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q3. How can I activate any new addon?</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: Through AKASH Self-care or by calling AKASH Hotline number 16442.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q4. How will I get the cashback?</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: Cashback will be given in your AKASH account within 05 August 2021.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q5. I already have Entertainment Add on (or any other), but I didn’t recharge it. Will I get the cashback if I recharge now?</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: No. But you can get the cashback if you take any other cashback (Like Sports or Kids add on etc.)</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q6. I am currently availing 1-month free offer for 6 months recharge, how can I get this offer?</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: You need to recharge for 7 months for an Add on to activate it. Then you will get the cashback equal to 100% of 1-month recharge of your add on.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q7. What will be the cashback amounts?</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: For Entertainment Pack Add on: BDT 75</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Infotainment Pack Add on: BDT 45</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Sports Pack Add on: BDT 71</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Kids Pack Add on: BDT 30</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Infotainment Pack 2 Add on: BDT 21</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q8. Can I avail other campaigns and offers if I take this offer?</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: Yes, you can avail this offer on top of any other offers or campaigns.</span></span></span></p>\n', '1625578744-733233.jpg', '1625578744-51737343.jpg', '', 'Offer', 0, 0, 1, '2021-07-06 23:55:21', '2021-07-31 23:55:21', '2021-07-06 20:34:22', '2021-07-06 19:39:05', ''),
(70, 'Eid ul Adha Recharge Fest', 'eid-ul-adha-recharge-fest', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">On this holy occasion of Eid ul Adha, AKASH brings more happiness to its subscribers. Any customer recharging exactly <strong>BDT 601</strong> within the campaign period will get a fixed <strong>BDT 60</strong> cashback to his/her AKASH Account. The customer can avail this offer as many times as he/she wants during the campaign period. </span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Besides, if the customer recharges through AKASH Selfcare, he/she will get <strong>additional BDT 40</strong>. That means, by recharging exactly <strong>BDT 601</strong> through <strong>AKASH Selfcare</strong> customer will get <strong>BDT 100 Cashback</strong>. </span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Registration link for AKASH Selfcare</strong>: t.ly/kEkj</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Campaign Duration:</strong> 11 &ndash; 31 July, 2021</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Terms &amp; Conditions:</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<ol>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Cashbacks will be given to customer&rsquo;s AKASH account within 7 working days from recharge.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Customer needs to recharge exactly BDT 601 for the offer.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">A subscriber can recharge as many times as he/she wants. There&rsquo;s no restriction on the number of recharges a subscriber can make during the campaign period. Every time he/she can avail this offer.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Customer will get additional BDT 40 if he/she recharges through AKASH Selfcare. In that case total Cashback amount will be BDT 100.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Successive recharges will NOT be counted &amp; treated as a single recharge. For instance, if a subscriber recharges BDT 400 and then BDT 201, he will not get the cashback. Customer needs to recharge BDT 601 in a single recharge.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">The cashback amount can be used for consumption in packages, add on packs etc. permitted by AKASH.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">This campaign does not depend on other campaigns as any customer can avail other campaign offers as well as Eid ul Adha Recharge Fest campaign offer by recharging exactly BDT 601 in his/her AKASH account within campaign period. </span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">AKASH reserves all rights to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</span></span></li>\n</ol>\n', '1626074313-651440.jpg', '1626074313-46264336.jpg', '', 'Offer', 0, 0, 1, '2021-07-12 12:15:00', '2021-07-31 23:55:00', '2021-07-12 13:29:29', '2021-07-12 13:18:33', ''),
(71, 'Post Eid 100% Cashback Campaign', 'post-eid-100-cashback', '<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">A campaign for the customers where anyone purchasing new AKASH connection from <strong>23 &ndash; 31 July, 2021</strong> and recharging his/her subscription pack within 7 August,2021 for at least one month will get 100% cashback of the one-month subscription pack amount in his/her AKASH Account.</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Campaign Timeline:</strong> 23 &ndash; 31 July, 2021</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Modality:</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<ol>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Customer can buy new AKASH connection from any retail point, website, call Center or partner store to avail this campaign offer.</span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Customer has to purchase new connection during campaign timeline and has to recharge within <strong>7<sup>th</sup> August, 2021</strong> of his subscription pack amount to avail the cashback. After 7<sup>th</sup> August the recharge would be considered invalid, and no cashback would be given in reference to the same. </span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Cashback will be disbursed within 7 working days after 7<sup>th</sup> August (Last recharge date).</span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Customer has to recharge at least one month of his subscription pack amount of the pack he/she purchased.</span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">&nbsp;If all the criteria are fulfilled customer will get 100% cashback of one month of his/her subscription pack amount. (If Lite Pack then 249/=, if Lite Plus Pack, then 300/=, if Standard Pack then 399/=)</span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">&nbsp;Any amount of cashback given under this campaign cannot be uncashed or transferred by the beneficiary and it&rsquo;s not related to any other campaign or discount of AKASH </span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">AKASH reserves all the right to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</span></span></li>\n</ol>\n', '1626702187-93587130.jpg', '1626702187-29279986.jpg', '', 'Offer', 0, 1, 1, '2021-07-22 23:55:59', '2021-07-31 23:55:00', '2021-07-19 19:43:07', '2021-07-19 19:43:07', ''),
(72, 'August Addon Campaign', 'august-addon-campaign', '<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">BDT 25 cashback on new Infotainment Pack-2 activation which is available only at BDT 21/month.</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Infotainment Pack-2 consists of 5 exclusive channels: </span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Sony BBC Earth</span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">NDTV 24/7</span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Wion News</span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">NDTV Good Times</span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">FOX Life (New Inclusion)</span></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">AKASH brings this lucrative cashback offer on the new addition of this pack. Now, AKASH Standard customers can also upgrade their subscription by adding Infotainment pack 2. </span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Upon successful addition and activation of new Infotainment Pack-2, customers will get <strong>BDT 25 Cashback.</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\