he can avail this offer. </span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Cashbacks will be given to customer&rsquo;s AKASH Account within 5 September, 2021.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Customer might NOT get any cashback if he/she removes the addon pack before the campaign ends or if his/her Addon or subscription is INACTIVE on 1 September 2021.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">AKASH reserves all rights to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</span></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', '1628171744-53281350.jpg', '1628171745-69939116.jpg', '', 'Offer', 0, 0, 1, '2021-08-07 23:55:00', '2021-08-31 23:55:00', '2021-08-05 19:55:45', '2021-08-05 19:55:45', ''),
