ampaign (i.e., from 9 Aug to 31 Aug), he/she will NOT be eligible for this campaign.</span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Customer can upgrade their packages from AKASH web self-care or by calling 16442.</span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Customer must migrate to get the cashback. Only recharging the migration amount will not initiate the offer.<a name=\"_Hlk71452476\"></a></span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">AKASH reserves all rights to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</span></span></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', '1628428220-90266295.jpg', '1628428221-59655550.jpg', '', 'Offer', 0, 0, 1, '2021-08-08 23:55:46', '2021-08-31 23:55:46', '2021-08-08 19:10:21', '2021-08-08 19:10:21', '');
