ht:50px; vertical-align:top; width:30%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">When will I receive the cashback after recharging?</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:50px; vertical-align:top; width:62%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">The cashback will be disbursed to your account instantly.</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:74px; vertical-align:top; width:6%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">7</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:74px; vertical-align:top; width:30%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">I did not recharge during the campaign period, but my account was active. Will I get any offer/cashback?</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:74px; vertical-align:top; width:62%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">If you did not recharge during the campaign, but were active you will receive an adjustment to your AKASH account. The adjustment/cashback will depend on your package, and the number of days your account was active during clean feed blackout period. The adjustment will be provided after 30<sup>th</sup> November. However, AKASH Lite Subscribers will not get any adjustment.</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:50px; vertical-align:top; width:6%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">8</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:50px; vertical-align:top; width:30%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Who will receive the adjustment at the end of the month?</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:50px; vertical-align:top; width:62%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">If you did not recharge during the Instant cashback campaign, and had AKASH Standard or AKASH Lite Plus, but were active during clean feed blackout period, you will receive an adjustment.</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:50px; vertical-align:top; width:6%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">9</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:50px; vertical-align:top; width:30%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">What is the maximum amount of adjustment I will receive if I did not recharge during the campaign (and was active)?</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:50px; vertical-align:top; width:62%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">The maximum amounts are: BDT 50 for AKASH Standard, BDT 25 for AKASH Lite Plus.</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:50px; vertical-align:top; width:6%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">10</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:50px; vertical-align:top; width:30%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">How will my adjustment be calculated?</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:50px; vertical-align:top; width:62%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Your adjustment will be calculated based on two factors: your package and the number of days you were active during November clean feed blackout.</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:50px; vertical-align:top; width:6%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">11</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:50px; vertical-align:top; width:30%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">I have availed the recharge cashback offer. Will I get any Adjustment?</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:50px; vertical-align:top; width:62%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">No, you will get the manual adjustment only if you did not recharge during the campaign period, and you were active during the November Clean Feed Blackout period.</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:50px; vertical-align:top; width:6%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">12</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:50px; vertical-align:top; width:30%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">I was inactive throughout October, and did not recharge. Will I receive any adjustment?</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:50px; vertical-align:top; width:62%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">You will need to be active during November clean feed blackout to be eligible for the manual adjustment.</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:50px; vertical-align:top; width:6%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">13</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:50px; vertical-align:top; width:30%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">I have recharged for 6 months/12 months. What will be my cashback?</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:50px; vertical-align:top; width:62%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">If you recharge during the period, you will receive a cashback (the amount will be as mentioned above.) If you do not recharge, but were active, you will receive an adjustment based on your package and the number of days you were active during clean feed blackout.</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n', '1635683052-68056129.jpg', '1635683053-5801907.jpg', '', 'Offer', 0, 1, 1, '2021-10-31 23:55:22', '2021-11-07 23:55:22', '2021-10-31 18:56:51', '2021-10-11 13:51:53', ''),
(87, 'Fan Jersey Campaign', 'fan-jersey-campaign', '<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">AKASH has launched an exclusive campaign for its customers on the occasion of T20 Cricket World Cup 2021. Anyone purchasing new AKASH connection from AKASH retail/website/call center/partner store or their website within 13 Oct – 14 Nov,2021 will get Bangladesh National Cricket Team’s T20 Captain Mahmudullah Riyad’s signed Fan Jersey for free with the connection. For every connection/STB purchase customer will get a jersey. </span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong>Campaign Timeline: </strong>13 October – 14 November, 2021</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong>Modality:</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Customer purchasing from any AKASH touch point will receive the jersey from the store with the connection/STB</span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Customer purchasing from website/online partner store/call center will get his/her jersey from the installer carrying the jersey on the installation day</span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Mahmudullah Riyad’s digital signature has been printed on the back of the fan jersey</span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">For query call 16442</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', '1634040556-7213672.jpg', '1634040556-43021390.jpg', '', 'Offer', 0, 1, 1, '2021-10-12 23:55:30', '2021-11-14 23:55:30', '2021-10-13 17:13:19', '2021-10-12 18:09:16', ''),
(88, 'Fan Jersey Recharge Campaign', 'fan-jersey-recharge-campaign', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">On the occasion of T20 World Cup 2021, for the delight of the cricket fans, AKASH brings a FAN JERSEY to watch World Cup in the true HD quality of AKASH.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Any AKASH subscriber can now get a FAN JERSEY by recharging exactly BDT 999 during this campaign. </span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Campaign Duration:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\"> 15 October &ndash; 14 November 2021</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Terms &amp; Conditions:</span></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<ol>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Customer must recharge exactly BDT 999 in his AKASH account.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Customers will be communicated after the recharge for his address and consent to receive the jersey.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-siz