(89, 'Riyad-Mushi World Cup Recharge Campaign', 'Riad-Mushi-World-Cup-Recharge-Campaign', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">On the occasion of T20 World Cup 2021, for the delight of the fans of Mahmudullah Riyad and Mushfiqur Rahim, AKASH brings a special cashback offer!</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Anybody recharging BDT 500 on Bangladesh’s match day will receive a cashback equal to total runs scored by Mahmudullah and Mushfiq together.</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>Campaign Duration:</strong> 17 October – 14 November 2021</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>Terms & Conditions:</strong></span></p>\n\n<ol>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Customer must recharge exactly BDT 500 in his AKASH account.</span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Customer needs to recharge on the <strong>Match-day</strong> for that day’s cashback </span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>(From 12:00 AM to 11:59 PM)</strong></span></p>\n\n<ol start=\"3\">\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:black\">Cashback amount will be equal to the total runs scored by Mushfiqur Rahim and Mahmudullah Riyad in that respective match.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Cashback will be given within 5 working days after the match.</span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">A customer can recharge as many times he wants. For every recharge of BDT 500, he will be entitled for the cashback.</span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">This offer will be applicable on top of all other offers applicable for the customer.</span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">AKASH reserves all rights to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Campaign FAQs:</strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\n\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"MsoTableGrid\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; border:none; width:100.0%\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"background-color:#d9e2f3; border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:1px solid black; vertical-align:top; width:6%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"background-color:#d9e2f3; border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:1px solid black; vertical-align:top; width:34%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Question</span></strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"background-color:#d9e2f3; border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:1px solid black; vertical-align:top; width:59%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Answer</span></strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:6%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>Q1.</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:34%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">How can I avail Riad-Mushi World Cup Recharge Offer?</span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:59%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">By recharging exactly BDT 500 to your AKASH account on the match day of Bangladesh in T20 World Cup 2021.</span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:6%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>Q2.</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:34%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">How many times I can recharge?</span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:59%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">You can recharge as many times you want. You will get the cashback for every recharge of BDT 500.</span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:6%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>Q3.</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:34%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">What is the cut off time for the recharge?</span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:59%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">You need to recharge within the Match-day <strong>for that day’s cashback</strong> (From 12:00 AM to 11:59 PM)</span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:6%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>Q4.</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:34%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">What will be the cashback amount?</span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:59%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:black\">Cashback will be equal to the total runs scored by Mushfiqur Rahim and Mahmudullah Riyad in that match.</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:6%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>Q4.</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:34%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">When will I get the cashback?</span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:59%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Within 5 working days, cashback will be given to your AKASH account.</span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Different Possible Scenarios-</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><em><u>Scenario 1</u></em><em>: </em>Match- <strong>Bangladesh VS Scotland, Oct 17 (Sunday)</strong></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">A customer recharges exactly BDT 500 on 17<sup>th</sup> Oct at 5:00pm.</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif; font-size:18px\">Mahmudullah scores- 35 runs & Mushfiq scores – 30 runs</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif; font-size:18px\">Total </span><strong>BDT 65 cashback</strong><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif; font-size:18px\"> will be given to the customer’s AKASH account by 24</span><sup>th</sup><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif; font-size:18px\"> Oct.</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><em><u>Scenario 2</u></em><em>: </em>Match -<strong>Bangladesh VS Oman, Oct 19 (Tuesday)</strong></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">A customer recharges exactly BDT 500 TWICE (BDT 500 + BDT 500) on 19<sup>th</sup> Oct at 9:00am.</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Mahmudullah scores- 40 runs & Mushfiq scores – 41 runs</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Total BDT 81 + 81 = <strong>BDT 162 cashback</strong> will be given to the customer’s AKASH account by 24<sup>th</sup> Oct.</span></p>\n', '1634213111-38008745.jpg', '1634213111-768445.jpg', '', 'Offer', 0, 0, 0, '2021-10-16 18:55:06', '2021-11-14 23:55:06', '2021-11-06 08:13:46', '2021-10-14 18:05:12', ''),
(90, '10-Day Free Period Extension', '10-day-free-period-extension', '<p>The 10-day free period will be applicable for customers whose account was created after the effective from date. The customers whose accounts were created before this time, even if their account was activated after the effective from date, will have the 5-day free period.</p>\n\n<p>Furthermore, this free period will be applicable for all packs.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Duration: </strong>1<strong>&nbsp;</strong>November &ndash; 07 January, 2022</p>\n\n<p><strong>Detailed Modalities:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Customers acquired after 1<strong>&nbsp;</strong>November will be eligible for the 10-day free period. After expiry of that, the customer&rsquo;s account will become inactive if there is no balance.</li>\n	<li>Accounts created after 07 January, 2022 will have the 5-day free period.</li>\n	<li>The 10-day free period will be available for AKASH Standard, Lite Plus and Lite packages.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>FAQ</p>\n\n<table cellspacing=\"0\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p><strong>Sl No.</strong></p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p><strong>Question</strong></p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p><strong>Answer</strong></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p>1</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>Who will be eligible for the 10-day free period?</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>If the customer account was <strong>created</strong> after 31&nbsp;October, 12:00AM, the customer will be eligible for the 10-day free period. If the customer account was created before this time, but activated later, the customer will only get the 5-day free period.</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p>2</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>The customer&#39;s account was activated on 1 November. Why did the customer not get the 15-day free period?</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>The customer&#39;s account was created before 1 November, 12:00AM, which was before the new free period launch date. Hence, the customer will get only the 5-day free period.</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p>3</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>For how long will the 10-day free period be available?</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>This 10-day free period will be applicable till 07 January, 2022.</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p>4</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>Will the activation of this 10-day period require any additional steps?</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>No, the customer will automatically get a 10-day free period if the account was created after 31&nbsp;October, 12:00AM.</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p>5</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>Which packages can the customer get the 10-day free period with?</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>The 10-day free period will be available for all packages.</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n', '1638941673-40361121.jpg', '1638941673-40103822.jpg', '', 'Offer', 0, 1, 1, '2021-11-01 00:55:13', '2022-01-07 23:55:13', '2021-12-31 10:33:51', '2021-10-14 22:16:19', '');
