4c4c5b\">The discount offer is not available on the STB rather on the whole connection (CPE).</span></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:#4c4c5b\">Strategic partners will have their own campaign. For single CPE purchase through strategic partner this offer will be applicable if they are not offering a better offer than BDT 500 discount. Otherwise, for bundle offer pack they will have their own campaign and this discount offer will not be applicable.</span></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:#4c4c5b\">To be eligible for cashback, customers have to activate the connection, recharge 3/6/12 months in one transaction (applicable for first recharge only) within 7<sup>th</sup> April&rsquo;22 . &nbsp;Subscribers has to recharge the full amount in one transaction.</span></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:#4c4c5b\">Customers would receive the cashback amount in their AKASH account on 11<sup>th</sup> April&rsquo;22.</span></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:#4c4c5b\">To avail this offer customer has to purchase the AKASH connection within the campaign period, installation and first recharge has to be done within 7<sup>th</sup> April&rsquo;22. Customer must call in Call Center (just before or after recharge) to change desired 3/6/12 months Billing Term to receive cashback on 11<sup>th</sup> April&rsquo;22.</span></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:#4c4c5b\">After 7<sup>th</sup> April&rsquo;22recharge would be considered invalid for this campaign, and no cashback can be provided in reference to the same.</span></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:#4c4c5b\">Any amount of cashback given under this campaign cannot be uncashed or transferred by the beneficiary.</span></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:#4c4c5b\">One customer can avail one offer (acquisition/ recharge) at a time. But the same customer can avail the referral offer and cashback.</span></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:#4c4c5b\">AKASH reserves all the right to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</span></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:71px; margin-right:38px; text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '1646054117-46594076.jpg', '1646054118-93607754.jpg', '1646054117-46594076.jpg', 'Offer', 1, 1, 1, '2022-02-28 23:55:18', '2022-03-31 23:55:18', '2022-03-29 13:42:46', '2022-02-28 19:15:18', ''),
(107, 'Independence Month Recharge Offer', 'Independence-Month-Recharge-Offer', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">March is the month of Glory and Pride for Bangladesh. We evolved as an independent nation on 26 March 1971. This year we mark the 51<sup>st</sup> anniversary of our Independence. On this occasion, AKASH brings an exciting recharge offer for its valued customers.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Offer: </span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Any customer recharging BDT 500 taka from 1 March to 31 March 2022 will get a BDT 51 Instant cashback in their AKASH Account. The customer can avail this offer as many times as s/he wants during the campaign period.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">On top of that, if the customer recharges BDT 500 or more through </span><strong><em><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">tap</span></em></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\"> App or USSD (only once), s/he will get additional BDT 50 Instant Cashback in his </span><strong><em><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">tap</span></em></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\"> wallet.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Campaign Duration:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\"> 1 March 2022 to 31 March 2022 (31 days)</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">*<strong><em>tap</em></strong> cashback will be available only <em>ONCE</em> from 11 March to 31 March 2022</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Terms &amp; Conditions:</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">All the customers of AKASH are eligible for this offer.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">BDT 51 Cashback will be given to customer&rsquo;s <strong>AKASH</strong> account instantly after recharge.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Customer needs to recharge exactly BDT 500 for the offer.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">A subscriber can recharge as many times as he/she wants. There&rsquo;s no restriction on the number of recharges a subscriber can make during the campaign period. Every time he/she can avail this offer. </span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Successive partial recharges will NOT be counted &amp; treated as a single recharge. For instance, if a subscriber recharges BDT 400 and then BDT 100, he will not get the cashback. Customer needs to recharge BDT 500 in a single recharge.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">On top of this offer, from 11 March to 31 March 2022, if a customer recharges BDT 500 or more through <strong><em>tap app/USSD </em></strong>he will get additional BDT 50 Instant cashback (Only once) in his/her <strong><em>tap </em></strong>account</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">AKASH</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\"> cashback amount can be used for consumption in packages, add on packs etc. permitted by AKASH.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">AKASH</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\"> reserves all rights to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Campaign FAQs:</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Q1. How can I avail BDT 51 cashback offer?</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Ans: By recharging BDT 500 to your Akash account in a single recharge within 1 Mar 2022 to 31 Mar 2022.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Q2. Where will the customer get this cashback?</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Ans: Cashback will be instantly given to your Akash account. </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Q3. When can I avail this offer?</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Ans: You can avail this offer by recharging BDT 500 to your Akash account in a single recharge withi<em>n 1 &ndash; 31 March 2022.</em></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Q4. When will I get the <strong>AKASH</strong> cashback?</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Ans: Cashbacks will be given Instantly to your AKASH Account. </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Q5. Can I avail this offer more than once?</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Ans: Yes, you can avail this offer as many times as you want within the campaign period by recharging 500 taka every time. </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Q6. During campaign, if I recharge fractionally (not at a time) to make it BDT 500, will I get the cashback?</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Ans: Fractional recharges will NOT be counted &amp; treated as a single recharge. For instance, if you recharge BDT 400 and then BDT 100, you will not get the cashback. You need to recharge BDT 500 at a single recharge to get the cashback.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Q7. What if I recharge more than BDT 500?</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Ans: You can only avail this offer if your recharge amount is <strong><em>exactly</em></strong> BDT 500. You will not get any cashback if you recharge more or less than BDT 500</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Q8. Will other offers be applicable for me if I avail this offer or vice versa?</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Ans: Yes, you can avail this offer on top of all other offers.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Q9. What is tap offer for this Campaign?</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Ans: You will get additional BDT 50 Instant Cashback in your tap Wallet if you recharge BDT 500 or more in AKASH DTH through tap app or USSD. That means, Recharging EXACTLY BDT 500 from tap, you will get BDT 51 Cashback in AKASH Account and another BDT 50 Cashback in tap wallet. But tap offer can be available only once from a single tap Account.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Q10. I have multiple AKASH but 1 tap account, how many times I will receive the cashback?</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">For AKASH wallet customer will receive cashback as many times as he will recharge during campaign period. For tap wallet customer will receive BDT 50 instant cashback for once.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Q11. Why didn&rsquo;t I receive tap cashback?</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Ans: For any complaints related to <strong><em>tap</em></strong> cashback in tap account: Call 16733 (from any number) **Charge Applicable Or email: </span><a href=\"mailto:complaint@trustaxiatapay.com\" style=\"color:#0563c1; text-decoration:underline\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">complaint@trustaxiatapay.com</span></a></span></span></p>\r\n', '1646054827-46831952.jpg', '1646054827-17419815.jpg', '', 'Offer', 0, 0, 1, '2022-02-28 23:55:53', '2022-03-31 23:55:53', '2022-03-15 12:03:27', '2022-02-28 19:27:07', ''),
(108, 'Standard Upgrade Campaign', 'Standard-Upgrade-Campaign', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">In the month of March 2022, any customer can get lucrative cashback offers by upgrading their packages to a higher pack!</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>Offer:</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">A customer can get <strong>BDT 100 Cashback</strong> by upgrading from <em>AKASH Lite</em> to AKASH Standard Pack.</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">A customer can get <strong>BDT</strong> <strong>50 Cashback </strong>by upgrading from <em>AKASH Lite Plus</em> to AKASH Standard Pack.</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Cashback Amount Table:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table align=\"center\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"MsoTableGrid\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; border:none; width:100.0%\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"background-color:#dbdbdb; border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:1px solid black; vertical-align:top; width:50%px\">\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>Previous Pack</strong></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"background-color:#dbdbdb; border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:1px solid black; vertical-align:top; width:50%px\">\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Upgrade to AKASH Standard</span></strong></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:50%px\">\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">AKASH Lite</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:50%px\">\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">BDT 100 Cashback</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:50%px\">\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">AKASH Lite Plus</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:50%px\">\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">BDT 50 Cashback</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>Campaign Duration:</strong> 1 March &ndash; 31 March 2022 (31 days) </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>Terms and Conditions:</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">New customers on-boarded after 28 February 2022 will NOT be eligible for this offer.</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Cashback will be given to customer&rsquo;s AKASH account <strong>within 15 working days </strong>of successful upgradation.</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">AKASH Lite or AKASH Lite Plus Customers can get a cashback by upgrading their package to AKASH Standard: BDT 100 for upgrading from <em>Lite to Standard</em>, BDT 50 for <em>Lite Plus to Standard.</em></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Customer&rsquo;s <strong>upgraded package must be ACTIVE till the end of the campaign</strong> (i.e.,31 March 2022) to get the cashback.</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">If a customer down-migrates his package to AKASH Lite or AKASH Lite Plus at ANY time during the campaign (i.e., from 1 Mar to 31 Mar 2022), he/she will NOT be eligible for this campaign.</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Customer can upgrade their packages from AKASH web self-care or by calling 16442.</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Customer must Upgrade and Activate AKASH Standard package get the cashback. Only recharging the migration amount will NOT initiate the offer.</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Only recharge will also NOT initiate the offer. For example, if a customer has recharged BDT 400, then he/she will NOT get the cashback. Customers MUST migrate their package by calling 16442 or through Web self-care.</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Customers who bought AKASH after Feb 28, or if their package is INACTIVE after upgradation, they will NOT get the cashback even if they migrate.</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">AKASH reserves all rights to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '1646055583-18650549.jpg', '1646055583-13327.jpg', '', 'Offer', 0, 0, 1, '2022-02-28 23:55:52', '2022-03-31 23:55:52', '2022-03-23 07:38:18', '2022-02-28 19:39:43', '');
