\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">A: No. Customer needs to recharge minimum BDT 1200 in a single transaction.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Q5: What is the conditions and benefit amount for Multi TV?&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">A: BDT 200 for BDT 1200 recharge in a single transaction.</span></span></p>\r\n', '1668697229-76119606.jpg', '1668697229-13397883.jpg', '1668697229-42398830.jpg', 'Offer', 1, 0, 1, '2022-11-19 23:55:39', '2022-12-18 23:55:40', '2022-11-17 21:00:29', '2022-11-17 21:00:29', 'Recharge'),
(142, 'Goal by Goal Cashback!', 'Goal-by-Goal-cashback', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">On the occasion of the FIFA World Cup, AKASH Brings an exciting recharge campaign for its valued customers. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Any customer recharging BDT 701 on a FIFA World Cup match day will receive a BDT 10 cashback for each goal of that day.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong>Campaign Duration:</strong> 20 November &ndash; 18 December 2022 (only on FIFA World Cup match days)</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong>Terms &amp; Conditions:</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Customer must recharge exactly BDT 701 in his AKASH account.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Customer needs to recharge within the Match-day for that day&rsquo;s cashback (From 12:00 AM to 11:59 PM)</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Cashback amount will be equal to the total goals scored on that day and multiplied by 10.</span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Example: If there are 5 matches, and total goals will 10, total cashback amount will be BDT 100 (10 goal X10 cashback).</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"4\">\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Cashback will be given within 5 working days after the match.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">A customer can recharge as many times as he wants. For every recharge of BDT 701, he will be entitled for the cashback</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">This offer will be applicable on top of all other offers applicable for the customer.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Goals on tie-breakers will not be counted for cashback. </span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Goals at 90 mins (with injury time/stoppage time: time that the referee adds to the end of each half of a game) match time will be calculated for cashback.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">If there is no FIFA World Cup match on a day, there will be no cashback for that day.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">If there is no goal scored in all matched in a particular day, customer will get BDT 30 cashback.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Starting time of the match will be considered on that day&#39;s match cashback. </span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">AKASH reserves all rights to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong>Campaign FAQs:</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Q1. How can I avail FIFA World Cup Recharge offer?</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Ans: By recharging exactly BDT 701 to your Akash account on the FIFA World Cup match day, you will get BDT 10 cashback for each goal of that day.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Q2. How many times I can recharge?</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Ans: You can recharge as many times you want. You will get the cashback for every recharge of BDT 701.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Q3. What is the cut off time for the recharge?</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Ans: You need to recharge within the Match-day for that day&rsquo;s cashback (From 12:00 AM to 11:59 PM)</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Q4. What will be the cashback amount?</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Ans: For every BDT 701 recharge on the match day, cashback amount will be equal to the total goals scored on that day and multiplied by 10.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Example: If there are 4 matches, and total goals will 12, total cashback amount will be BDT 120.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Q5. When will I get the cashback?</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Ans: within 5 working days, cashback will be given to your AKASH account.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Q6: For multiple matched in a single day what will be the cashback amount.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Ans: Cashback amount will be equal to the total goals scored on that day and multiplied by 10.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Example: If there are 5 matches, and total goals will 10, total cashback amount will be BDT 100.</span></span></p>\r\n', '1668697576-32012527.jpg', '1668697576-34933875.jpg', '1668697576-80211049.jpg', 'Offer', 1, 0, 1, '2022-11-19 23:55:36', '2022-12-18 23:55:36', '2022-11-17 21:06:16', '2022-11-17 21:06:16', 'Recharge'),
(143, 'BDT 600 savings on new AKASH connection by City Bank American® Express Cards', 'BDT-600-savings-on-new-AKASH-connection', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">On the occasion of the FIFA World Cup, <strong><span style=\"color:black\">City Bank American® Express </span></strong>cardholders can now enjoy exclusive discount when they purchase new AKASH BASIC connection from AKASH website. Under the campaign, City Bank American® Express cardholders will get BDT 600 (Six Hundred) discount for E-commerce transactions on new connection purchase from <span style=\"color:black\">MyAKASH App</span>/AKASH website: <a href=\"http://www.akashdth.com\" style=\"color:#0563c1; text-decoration:underline\">www.akashdth.com</a>. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">This new connection purchase offer includes 1 month’s subscription fee. The total price of this bundle offer is BDT 4899/- (Four Thousand Eight Hundred Ninety-Nine Taka Only) and eligible City Bank American® Express Cardholder shall pay BDT 4299/- (Four Thousand Two Hundred Ninety-Nine Taka Only) only after availing the discount offer of BDT 600/- (Six Hundred Taka Only).</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Campaign Timeline: </strong>25 November – 20 December 2022</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Consumer Offer Modality:</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Customer need to purchase a specific combo product of BASIC connection Full CPE with one-month AKASH STANDARD Package at BDT 4,899.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Customer will get BDT 600 discount through </span>City Bank American® Express <span style=\"color:black\">card payment. </span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Customers need to purchase through </span><span style=\"color:black\">MyAKASH App/AKASH website </span>(www.akashdth.com)<span style=\"color:black\">.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Customers can avail the offer unlimited time throughout the campaign period. </span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">AKASH and CBL reserve all rights to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>FAQ:</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Q1: Which cards are applicable? </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">A: Payment through City Bank American® Express Credit Cards only (Fixed BIN Number)</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Q2: From where can I avail this offer? (AKASH website/My AKASH App/Self care/ Other websites/ Other apps?)        </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">A: From MyAKASH App/AKASH website: <a href=\"http://www.akashdth.com\" style=\"color:#0563c1; text-decoration:underline\">www.akashdth.com</a>.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Q3: Is this offer applicable for both POS and online payment?     </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">A: Only online payment</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Q4: What is the benefit amount? And how will customers get it? </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">A: Customers will get BDT 600 discount through City Bank American® Express card payment.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Q5: Will customer get this offer with EMI?           </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">A: No</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Q6: Applicable for any connection purchase? (Full CPE, only STB, Combo 2/3/4 connection etc.)</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">A: Customers need to purchase a specific combo product of BASIC connection Full CPE with one-month AKASH STANDARD Package at BDT 4,899.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Q7: If I only buy STB, will I get benefit in price?</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">A: No</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Q8: How many connections can a customer purchase with same card?</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">A: Customer can avail the offer for unlimited time within the campaign period.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Q9: Any restriction on saving card? </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">A: No</span></span></p>\r\n', '1669785838-66781332.jpg', '1669785838-51029327.jpg', '1669785838-44325733.png', 'Offer', 1, 0, 1, '2022-11-24 23:55:37', '2022-12-20 23:55:37', '2022-11-30 11:23:58', '2022-11-24 16:50:44', '');
