 conditions and benefit amount for Multi TV?&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">A: BDT 50 cashback for BDT 500 recharge in a single transaction.</span></span></p>\r\n', '1672832602-27393563.jpg', '1672832602-22292050.jpg', '1672832602-94107918.jpg', 'Offer', 1, 0, 1, '2023-01-01 00:00:01', '2023-01-31 23:55:01', '2023-01-16 08:55:23', '2023-01-04 17:43:22', 'Recharge'),
(147, 'BPL Match Day Offer', 'BPL-Match-Day-Offer', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">On the occasion of (Bangladesh Premier League) BPL T20 2023, AKASH brings a special cashback offer for its valued customers. </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Any customer recharging BDT 1200 on an BPL match day will receive a cashback equal to winning team&rsquo;s total score of that day.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Campaign Duration:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\"> 06 January &ndash; 17 February 2023 (only on BPL match days)</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Terms &amp; Conditions:</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Customer must recharge exactly BDT 1200 in his AKASH account.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Customer needs to recharge within the Match-day for that day&rsquo;s cashback (From 12:00 AM to 11:59 PM)</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Cashback amount will be equal to the winning team&rsquo;s total of that match on BPL.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Cashback amount will be equal to the highest team total among the teams playing on that day. Example: If there are 2 matches, Sylhet Strikers vs Chattogram Challengers and Cumilla Victorians vs Rangpur Riders, Cashback will be equal to the highest team total among these 4 teams.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Cashback will be given within 5 working days after the match.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">A customer can recharge as many times as he wants. For every recharge of BDT 1200, he will be entitled for the cashback</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">This offer will be applicable on top of all other offers applicable for the customer.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">If any match gets abandoned without a single ball bowled, customers recharging BDT 1200 will get BDT 120 cashback.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">If the match remains incomplete, cashback will be equal to highest team total of the completed part of the match.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">If there is no BPL match on a day, there will be no cashback for that day.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">If there are multiple recharge offers, customers will get the highest benefit among them on any single recharge.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">AKASH reserves all rights to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Campaign FAQs:</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Q1. How can I avail BPL Recharge offer?</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Ans: By recharging exactly BDT 1200 to your Akash account on the BPL match day, you will get the cashback equal to the highest Team total of that day (Winning team&rsquo;s score)</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Q2. How many times I can recharge?</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Ans: You can recharge as many times you want. You will get the cashback for every recharge of BDT 1200.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Q3. What is the cut off time for the recharge?</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Ans: You need to recharge within the Match-day for that day&rsquo;s cashback (From 12:00 AM to 11:59 PM)</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Q4. What will be the cashback amount?</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Ans: For every BDT 1200 recharge on the match day, cashback will be equal the highest Team total of that day (Winning team&rsquo;s score)</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Q5. When will I get the cashback?</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Ans: within 5 working days, cashback will be given to your AKASH account.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Q6: For multiple matched in a single day what will be the cashback amount.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Ans: Cashback amount will be equal to the highest team total among the teams playing on that day. Example: If there are 2 matches, Sylhet Strikers vs Chattogram Challengers and Cumilla Victorians vs Rangpur Riders, Cashback will be equal to the highest team total among these 4 teams.</span></span></span></p>\r\n', '1673497844-21776663.jpg', '1673497844-69045040.jpg', '1673497845-26074747.jpg', 'Offer', 1, 0, 1, '2023-01-05 23:55:21', '2023-02-17 23:55:23', '2023-01-15 20:03:52', '2023-01-06 08:38:40', 'Recharge'),
(148, '1+1 Subscription Offer on New Connection', 'Subscription-Offer-on-New-Connection', '<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">AKASH is offering an exciting Buy One Get One subscription campaign in the New Year 2023 where customers will get BDT 400 cashback after a new connection purchase and 1<sup>st</sup> month’s recharge. The campaign is applicable only for Standard Package customers. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Timeline: 16 – 31 January, 2023 </span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Terms & Conditions:</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Customers purchasing new connections and recharging 1st month’s Standard subscription within the campaign timeline will get BDT 400.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Offer is only applicable for standard package customers.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">BDT 400 Cashback will be disbursed instantly after recharge.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Customer must recharge the exact or more amount of the AKASH Standard pack. No partial or less amount (of his/her subscription package) will be eligible to avail of cashback.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">For 1<sup>st</sup> recharge on Standard Package only this offer is applicable, the customer will not get any other recharge offer benefit. </span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">If there are multiple recharge offers, customers will get the highest benefit among them on any single recharge.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">AKASH reserves the right to change, cancel or extend the offer at any time.</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '1673867149-47435951.jpg', '1673867149-61544584.jpg', '1673867149-60737761.jpg', 'Offer', 1, 1, 1, '2023-01-15 23:55:22', '2023-01-31 23:55:22', '2023-01-16 17:05:49', '2023-01-15 17:24:11', ''),
(150, 'Up to BDT 650 benefits on New Connection', 'Up-to-BDT-650-benefits-on-New-Connection', '<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">In the month of February customers will get exclusive benefits on the new AKASH connection. Customers can avail upto BDT 650 cashback during the campaign period. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">BDT 400 net discount on the MRP for AKASH connection. The campaign period price will be BDT 4,099 for AKASH Basic connection.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">On top of the discount in connection price customers purchasing new connections and recharging 1st month&rsquo;s in Standard subscription within the campaign timeline will get BDT 100 and on 2nd month&rsquo;s recharge will get BDT 50.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Additionally, if customer gets the AKASH Standard connection from referral, BDT 100 cashback will be provided to customer&rsquo;s AKASH account. <a href=\"https://akashdth.com/offers/Customer-Referral-Offer\">Click here</a> to see Rererral campaign details.&nbsp;</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Campaign Timeline: </strong>1 &ndash; 28 February 2023</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Terms &amp; Conditions:</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Customers have to buy AKASH connection from AKASH retail points, AKASH website or MyAKASH App within the campaign period.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">BDT 400 net discount on the MRP for AKASH connection. The campaign period price will be BDT 4,099 for AKASH Basic connection.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">The discount offer is not available on the STB rather on the whole connection (CPE).</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">On top of the discount in connection price customers purchasing new connections and recharging 1st month&rsquo;s Standard subscription within the campaign timeline will get BDT 100 and on 2nd month&rsquo;s recharge will get BDT 50.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Recharge offer is only applicable for standard package customers.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">First month&rsquo;s BDT 100 Cashback will be disbursed instantly after recharge.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Second month&rsquo;s BDT 50 cashback will be disbursed by April 11, 2023.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Second month&rsquo;s cashback will depend on the active status of the subscriber. Customer must recharge and be active on the second month to avail second month&rsquo;s BDT 50 cashback.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Customer must recharge the exact or more amount of the subscription pack he/she purchased and recharge to be eligible to avail both cashbacks. No partial or less amount (of his/her subscription package) will be eligible to avail cashback. </span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">For Long Duration Plan recharge (6/12 months) customer will get cashback within the mentioned timeline. No second recharge is required.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Additionally, if customer buys Standard package from referral of existing customer, BDT 100 cashback will be provided to customer&rsquo;s AKASH account. </span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">AKASH reserves the right to change, cancel or extend the offer at any time.</span></p>\r\n', '1675178272-68567523.jpg', '1675178272-14453697.jpg', '1675310231-47830737.png', 'Offer', 1, 1, 1, '2023-01-31 23:55:27', '2023-02-28 23:55:27', '2023-02-05 12:26:36', '2023-01-31 11:58:58', ''),
(151, 'Early Bird Offer!', 'Early-Bird-Offer!', '<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Recharge BDT 410 before the expiry date and every day lucky 20 subscribers will get 100% (BDT 410) cashback.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Campaign Timeline: </span></strong><span style=\"color:black\">01&nbsp;&ndash; 28 February, 2023</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Terms &amp; Conditions:</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Recharge amount will be exactly BDT 410.<strong> </strong></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Customer need to recharge before the expiry date. For example: If anyone&rsquo;s package expiry date is 10 February 2023, to get eligible for the offer customer needs to recharge within 09 February 2023, 11:59 PM.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Successive recharges will NOT be counted &amp; treated as a single recharge. For instance, if a Lite Package subscriber recharges BDT 200 and then BDT 210, he will not get the cashback. Customer needs to recharge BDT 410 in a single recharge.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Winner will be selected by lottery and the winner list will be publish on AKASH OFFERS Channel (LCN 101).</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">A Customer can get the reward only Once during the campaign if eligible.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Cashback amount in the AKASH account can be used for consumption in packages, add-on packs, etc. permitted by AKASH.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">AKASH reserves all rights to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">FAQ:</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Q1: How can I avail this offer? / What is the offer?&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">A: All AKASH Subscribers will get cashback on recharging BDT 410, and every day lucky 20 subscribers will get 100% (BDT 410) cashback.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Q2. Where will the customer get this cashback?</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Ans: Cashback will be instantly given to your Akash wallet. </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Q3. When will I get the cashback?</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Ans: Cashbacks will be given within 10 March 2023 to your AKASH Wallet. </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Q4. Can I avail this offer more than once?</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Ans: No. AKASH cashback will be available only once for a single AKASH Subscriber ID. </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Q5. During campaign, if I recharge fractionally (not at a time) to make the mentioned amount, will I get the cashback?</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Ans: Successive recharges will NOT be counted &amp; treated as a single recharge. For instance, if a Lite Package subscriber recharges BDT 200 and then BDT 210, he will not get the cashback. Customer needs to recharge BDT 410 in a single recharge.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Q6. What if I recharge more than the mentioned amount?</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Ans: You can only avail this offer if your recharge the </span><span style=\"color:black\">exact </span><span style=\"color:black\">amount. You will not get any cashback if you recharge more or less than the mentioned amount</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Q7. I have Multi TV. How many times I will get the cashback for each connection?</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Ans: You can only avail this offer once for mentioned amount recharge in your parent ID only.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '1675144957-85987247.jpg', NULL, NULL, 'recharge', 1, 0, 0, '2023-02-01 00:00:22', '2023-02-28 23:55:22', '2023-01-31 12:02:37', '2023-01-31 12:02:37', ''),
(152, 'Customer Referral Offer', 'Customer-Referral-Offer', '<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">When an AKASH subscriber refers AKASH to a potential customer, the referrer and referee both will get BDT 100 cashback in their AKASH account if the referee gets AKASH Standard Package. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Campaign Timeline: </strong>1 &ndash; 28 February 2023</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Terms &amp; Conditions:</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Both Referrer and the Referee will get BDT100 cashback (each) in their AKASH account if referee buys Standard package after referring new connection lead through contact center channel or MY AKASH APP</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Referred Sales lead must be confirmed, account is activated and recharge is made (e. g. One-month full subscription fees) in newly created Referee&rsquo;s account.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Sales Lead must need to be completed/ fulfilled (i.e., Purchase, Activate and Recharge) within 7th Day of following month from the Referred Date (Lead Issue date). Examples:</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Scenario 01: If any Referrer refers a lead on 01-Feb-2023, that lead must be completed the steps of Purchase, Activation and Recharge within 07-Mar-2023</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Scenario 02: If any Referrer refers a lead on 15-Feb-2023, that lead must be completed the steps of Purchase, Activation and Recharge within 07-Mar-2023</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Scenario 03: If any Referrer refers a lead on 28-Feb-2023, that lead must be completed the steps of Purchase, Activation and Recharge within 07-Mar-2023</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">One subscriber can get maximum BDT 500 as referrer in a calendar month or 5 referrals in a month based on Referred date (Lead Issue date)</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Referral bonus will be disbursed within 10 working days after the required recharge in newly created Referee&rsquo;s account.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">AKASH reserves all rights to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '1675353438-28657201.jpg', '1675353438-17642513.jpg', '1675353438-43584317.png', 'Offer', 1, 1, 1, '2023-01-31 23:55:31', '2023-02-28 23:55:31', '2023-02-05 08:56:09', '2023-02-02 16:09:53', '');
